    1180,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1',
    '{"id":"01KECYDK5VSRN6D84B88QK12GG","title":"Powerhouse Gym & Ideometry: Weekly Sync","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Campaign Transition and Management**\n\nThe marketing ads team has been let go, and **Nina Belina''s team will take over all marketing ads, including meta ads and SMS campaigns** starting immediately (05:33).\n\n- **The SMS campaign is currently in approval with HubSpot, expected to complete in 5 to 8 business days** (05:51)  \n    - The developer will finalize the trial campaign today, including non-indexed pages for meta ads forms.  \n    - Milan Wagner emphasized the need to track SMS automation approval closely since it impacts campaign launch timing.  \n    - Nina confirmed the developer has access to all required systems, ensuring no blockers remain.  \n    - The handover marks a shift from the previous ads team, requiring close coordination for a smooth transition.\n\n- **Trial campaign must launch as soon as possible and run continuously without offers, focusing on driving trial club visits** (13:24)  \n    - Milan specified the campaign will not include promotions but will target general trial awareness.  \n    - Separate campaigns with different offers, including group fitness content, will follow this baseline trial campaign.  \n    - Nina''s team will review and improve existing video and photo assets from prior marketing efforts to optimize ad performance.  \n    - Milan will provide all existing campaign materials and Dropbox access to support asset availability.\n\n- **On January 19th, the current zero enrollment promo campaign will be paused and replaced with a “dollar down + two weeks free” offer campaign focused on lead generation** (11:54)  \n    - Milan will send detailed promo information and campaign recommendations to Nina’s team.  \n    - Nina will consult with their paid media expert to decide whether to pause or update visuals for the transition.  \n    - The new campaign aims to maximize online leads for sales representatives to close.  \n    - This date allows a weekend buffer for preparation and ensures seamless promotion switching.\n\n## **Audience Targeting Strategy for Meta Ads**\n\nThe team agreed to delegate audience targeting decisions to Nina’s marketing team with only high-level guidance from Milan (07:01).\n\n- **Milan outlined basic location and age targeting: exclude under 18, target 18-50 tightly in Miami with a 2-3 mile radius, and extend up to age 65 with a 4-mile radius in Fort Lauderdale** (07:22)  \n    - This refined geographic approach aims to improve ad relevance and cost efficiency.  \n    - Milan deferred to the marketing team for selecting interests and detailed segments, emphasizing their expertise over his sales background.  \n    - Nina suggested conducting a short market research to identify optimal audience segments before locking targeting parameters.  \n    - Milan agreed with the approach to keep campaigns stable after launch to allow algorithms to optimize.\n\n- **Interest targeting will focus on gym, health, and fitness-related themes, but final criteria will be decided by Nina’s team with iterative optimization** (09:10)  \n    - Past campaigns by Ideometry provide a benchmark for targeting and creative strategy.  \n    - Milan requested regular updates on any targeting changes to monitor performance.  \n    - This flexible approach balances initial strategy with ongoing data-driven adjustments.\n\n## **System Integrations and Data Tracking**\n\nHubSpot and Meta integration is confirmed active, enabling accurate lead tracking, which is critical for measuring campaign ROI (08:26).\n\n- **HubSpot now communicates directly with Meta, allowing lead conversion tracking without additional connection setup** (08:44)  \n    - Milan wants a walkthrough of how data flows between platforms to monitor cost per lead and conversion rates.  \n    - Nina will request technical details from their developer to clarify the integration’s capabilities.  \n    - This integration reduces manual tracking work and improves attribution accuracy.  \n    - The ability to see which Meta leads close in HubSpot supports data-driven marketing decisions.\n\n- **The SMS automation remains in approval, causing slight delays, but should be resolved within the next week** (05:51)  \n    - Milan emphasized the importance of completing this to enable automated outreach for campaigns.  \n    - Nina confirmed the developer is ready to implement as soon as approval arrives.  \n    - Timely completion of the SMS setup directly impacts campaign effectiveness.\n\n## **Content and Asset Management**\n\nAccess and quality of marketing content are key for campaign success, with a focus on improving previous materials (14:02).\n\n- **Milan will provide Nina’s team with Dropbox access containing old and new photos and videos to maximize creative options** (15:20)  \n    - The previous marketing team’s videos and ad sets did not perform well, so Nina’s team will review and optimize them.  \n    - Nina’s team can make changes and will share updates with Milan for approval to ensure quality and alignment.  \n    - This content refresh aims to increase ad engagement and conversion rates.  \n    - Having a broad content library enables faster iteration and testing of different creative approaches.\n\n- **Nina’s developers will handle invisible pages setup for trial campaign forms on the website using existing Squarespace access** (17:47)  \n    - No additional support from Milan’s side is needed for website changes.  \n    - This setup ensures the forms remain unindexed to avoid SEO penalties while supporting ad tracking.  \n    - Efficient handling of form pages avoids delays in campaign launches.\n\n## **Campaign Workflow and Communication**\n\nClear processes and communication channels will support the transition and ongoing campaign management (16:44).\n\n- **Nina will coordinate with her paid media expert on campaign transitions and share recommendations on pausing or updating ads** (12:59)  \n    - Milan expects to receive all promo details and campaign materials promptly to meet the January 19th launch.  \n    - Nina will ask questions and provide updates via chat to maintain smooth communication.  \n    - This workflow supports quick decision-making and reduces turnaround time.  \n    - Milan remains available to provide clarifications or additional content as needed.\n\n- **The focus is on running only two active campaigns initially: the trial campaign and the new dollar down offer campaign** (18:23)  \n    - The older zero enrollment campaign will be paused without further review to streamline efforts.  \n    - This focus allows the team to allocate resources efficiently and measure campaign impact clearly.  \n    - Milan emphasized the importance of a “win” to build momentum.  \n    - Clear priorities improve team alignment and execution speed.","outline":null,"keywords":["HubSpot integration","Meta ads","SMS campaign","Trial campaign","Marketing transition","Campaign targeting"],"overview":"- **Marketing Team Transition:** Nina''s team takes over all marketing ads, including SMS campaigns, due to previous team''s layoffs.\n\n- **SMS Campaign Timeline:** Approval with HubSpot expected in 5-8 business days; trial campaign will focus on driving trial club visits.\n\n- **New Offer Launch:** Current zero enrollment promo pauses on January 19; replaced with “dollar down + two weeks free” campaign for lead generation.\n\n- **Audience Targeting Decisions:** Nina''s team to handle audience targeting, focusing on Miami and Fort Lauderdale; input from Milan for high-level guidance only.\n\n- **System Integration Active:** HubSpot integration with Meta confirmed; improves lead tracking and campaign ROI measurement, reducing manual efforts.\n\n- **Content Accessibility Improvement:** Milan will provide Dropbox access to old/new marketing assets; focus on optimizing previous materials to boost ad engagement.","action_items":"\n**Milan Wagner**\nSend all trial campaign and dollar down offer videos and photos to Marketing team for review and optimization (14:02)\nProvide Dropbox access with old and new content to Marketing team (15:16)\nShare detailed promo information and campaign launch instructions for January 19th new offer (12:36)\nConfirm with paid media expert about campaign switch strategy (pause/re-upload) and relay info to Marketing (12:59)\n\n**Nina Belina**\nMonitor SMS campaign approval status on HubSpot and report updates (05:43)\nCoordinate with developer to complete trial campaign setup and website form configurations (06:23)\nConduct market research and propose initial targeting criteria for Meta ads; run campaigns with iterative testing and adjustments (09:10)\nRequest detailed info from developer about HubSpot-Meta integration and how lead data is tracked/reviewed (08:26)\nConsult paid media person regarding best practices for pausing or updating running campaigns, then communicate guidance (12:59)\nManage launching the trial campaign immediately and prepare the new campaign for January 19 launch (13:24)\nEnsure developer handles invisible pages/forms for trial campaign on the website (17:47)\nTake responsibility for running and managing the two approved active campaigns; no need to review the campaign being shut down (18:05)\n"},"duration":19.670000076293945,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Nina Belina"},{"id":1,"name":"Milan Wagner"},{"id":2,"name":"Milan Wagner"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":328.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.2,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Hey Nina, how you doing?","index":1,"end_time":330.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.56,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Good, how are you?","index":2,"end_time":332.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.56,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Good, good.","index":3,"end_time":334.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":333.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And we let go of our marketing ads team yesterday.","index":4,"end_time":339.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":335.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So you guys are going to be helping us out with that.","index":5,"end_time":342.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":339.23,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That''s great.","index":6,"end_time":344.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.39,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"And I wanted to ask for the SMS campaign.","index":7,"end_time":348.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.75,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Did you get hear anything from HubSpot or.","index":8,"end_time":351.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.83,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"It''s.","index":9,"end_time":352.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":351.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I think it''s in the approval stage.","index":10,"end_time":354.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":352.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So if you, if you log into.","index":11,"end_time":356.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":354.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"HubSpot you can check that two seconds.","index":12,"end_time":362.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":356.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It takes five to eight business days.","index":13,"end_time":365.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.93,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, so the same day that I was like talking to you guys about how it was denied, we, I ended up fixing that and it''s still impending.","index":14,"end_time":377.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So yeah, there''s nothing really I can do on that.","index":15,"end_time":381.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":378.77,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We just have to wait.","index":16,"end_time":382.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.73,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, but I mean as soon as it''s clear damage to our developer should be able to do everything that''s necessary.","index":17,"end_time":390.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":383.33,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"He will also be finishing today the trial campaign.","index":18,"end_time":396.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.23,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The only things that he needs to set up are the non indexed pages for the forms for the meta ads on the website and, and that should be it.","index":19,"end_time":407.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.71,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"You guys are going to run all of that, right?","index":20,"end_time":412.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":410.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So you, well, now that you guys are doing our meta ads too, you''ll probably be posting and creating that campaign.","index":21,"end_time":419.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":413.15,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you have any additional like targets or anything that you want for that campaign?","index":22,"end_time":426.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":421,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because I don''t think that we talked about it in detail.","index":23,"end_time":429.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":426.52,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"What kind of additional targets?","index":24,"end_time":432.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":431.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So for example, like what audiences?","index":25,"end_time":435.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":433,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like the usual ones that you target in your other ads or do you have any other specifics.","index":26,"end_time":440.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"To be honest?","index":27,"end_time":442.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, I, I kind of want you guys to, to tell me that.","index":28,"end_time":450.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So age?","index":29,"end_time":453.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":452.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Nothing.","index":30,"end_time":454.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Under 18 in Miami.","index":31,"end_time":458.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I, I wouldn''t go anything over 50 in Fort Lauderdale.","index":32,"end_time":463.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It can go all the way up to like, I mean I don''t know how many people on Instagram that are over 50, but maybe let''s push it.","index":33,"end_time":471.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":463.35,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To 65 in Fort Lauderdale.","index":34,"end_time":473.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"In terms of location, Miami needs to be tighter.","index":35,"end_time":482.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":477.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I would do like three miles around Miami or two miles around Miami, the location.","index":36,"end_time":490.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":482.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then Fort Lauderdale can be a little larger.","index":37,"end_time":492.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":490.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So maybe four.","index":38,"end_time":493.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":492.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We need to be, we need to connect HubSpot to Meta as well.","index":39,"end_time":501.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"You need to walk me through that because I had, I did not understand your, your request.","index":40,"end_time":506.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":501.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Well, first I thought we needed to connect it because of that, but then I talked with our developer and he said that everything is set through HubSpot so now nothing should be added anymore.","index":41,"end_time":520.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.78,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we''re.","index":42,"end_time":521.929,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":521.369,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So HubSpot now talks to Meta?","index":43,"end_time":524.089,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":521.929,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, now it should be fine.","index":44,"end_time":525.689,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":524.249,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So it knows which meta leads close, that kind of stuff.","index":45,"end_time":530.889,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":526.489,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean I can ask him for more details, but from my, from my understanding, there''s nothing to be done there anymore.","index":46,"end_time":538.169,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.689,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, then I would like to know.","index":47,"end_time":541.169,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":539.049,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like how that works.","index":48,"end_time":542.249,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":541.169,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So whenever we can do that, that''d be great.","index":49,"end_time":546.009,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":543.049,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then I guess also for, for.","index":50,"end_time":550.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":547.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The med ads, like are there any specific interests that you usually target?","index":51,"end_time":555.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":550.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So for example, I don''t know, within.","index":52,"end_time":559.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.48,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The audience, anything gym related, health related, fitness related?","index":53,"end_time":564.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":559.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, what?","index":54,"end_time":573.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":570.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like, once again, I''m gonna like push.","index":55,"end_time":575.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573.25,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That over towards you guys.","index":56,"end_time":576.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":575.17,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I, I, I''m a sales expert.","index":57,"end_time":579.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":577.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I am not a marketing expert whatsoever.","index":58,"end_time":582.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.81,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So like, when it comes to those kind of criteria, I want you guys to suggest things and if they''re not.","index":59,"end_time":590.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":583.97,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Working, then suggest other things and we''ll just do it.","index":60,"end_time":592.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":590.01,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just keep us in the loop when, when we''re like making those kind of changes.","index":61,"end_time":597.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":593.57,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ideometry used to do our ads.","index":62,"end_time":604.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":599.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So like at the beginning of the year they were doing it.","index":63,"end_time":606.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":604.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So maybe you can have a look at those.","index":64,"end_time":607.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":606.22,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think it''ll be useful just to like make a short market research to see, you know, what''s the best moves and then when we have it set, so because we discussed it previously that you know, once you set it, you shouldn''t change it for a certain while.","index":65,"end_time":621.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.26,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So, you know, so we have like clear insights and then, you know, we can just leave it to, to for the algorithm to do its own thing.","index":66,"end_time":630.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":621.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Sounds good to me.","index":67,"end_time":632.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you have any other, you know, questions regarding HubSpot or integrations or anything.","index":68,"end_time":639.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":634.31,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"In terms of, I don''t know, air.","index":69,"end_time":643.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Call contacts, email address?","index":70,"end_time":645.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":643.03,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"No, no, not, I''m trying to think.","index":71,"end_time":649.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":646.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, not really.","index":72,"end_time":650.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":649.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If HubSpot''s talking to Meta, that was like one of the topics of conversation I wanted to have.","index":73,"end_time":656.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":652.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So if that''s working, then great, then.","index":74,"end_time":658.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.78,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Now we can like really track the cost per lead because we''ll know which ones are actually converting.","index":75,"end_time":662.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":658.42,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So that''s cool.","index":76,"end_time":664.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":663.98,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I just want to see how that works and where we can review that.","index":77,"end_time":668.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":664.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"On meta or on HubSpot?","index":78,"end_time":669.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":668.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Whichever one.","index":79,"end_time":670.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":669.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then I wanted to talk a lot about like meta ads.","index":80,"end_time":674.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":672.06,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So the trial campaign needs to go out and then there''s a change in the campaign in three days time.","index":81,"end_time":682.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":676.11,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That we need to take care of as well.","index":82,"end_time":686.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":684.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So on the, let''s do it on the 19th.","index":83,"end_time":690.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":686.83,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So on the 19th of January that.","index":84,"end_time":693.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":691.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Gives us the weekend as well.","index":85,"end_time":695.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":693.43,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We''re changing the promo from zero enrollment.","index":86,"end_time":699.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":696.51,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To a dollar down in two weeks free.","index":87,"end_time":702.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":700.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I''ll send you the details of the promo.","index":88,"end_time":704.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":702.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But the zero enrollment campaign needs to.","index":89,"end_time":708.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Be shut off, I guess, or paused, whatever.","index":90,"end_time":711.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":708.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And Then the new campaign needs to.","index":91,"end_time":713.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":711.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Be launched.","index":92,"end_time":714.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":713.88,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And the goal for that campaign is to drive as many leads as possible to join online and to.","index":93,"end_time":724.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Produce leads so that our reps can close them.","index":94,"end_time":730.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":725.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I will send you all of.","index":95,"end_time":733.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.54,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The details right now.","index":96,"end_time":738.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":733.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Add to be released on January 19th.","index":97,"end_time":749.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":743.7,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I just, I put in some.","index":98,"end_time":754.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":752.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Like recommendations on like what to put in there.","index":99,"end_time":756.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":754.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But listen, if you guys think it''s, it should be something different then do it on January I think.","index":100,"end_time":765.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":756.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":101,"end_time":778.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":777.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I will also ask our paid media person since you already have a campaign active, what''s the best move to do?","index":102,"end_time":786.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.18,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Like pause it or just you know, re upload the visuals and that.","index":103,"end_time":791.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":786.14,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So you know, whatever she says I will let you know.","index":104,"end_time":794.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":791.56,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So we would have the new campaign that starts from January 19th and the meta ad trial campaign.","index":105,"end_time":802.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":795.24,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yes, and the trial campaign.","index":106,"end_time":806.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":804.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The trial campaign needs to be launched.","index":107,"end_time":808.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"As soon as possible.","index":108,"end_time":809.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":808.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":109,"end_time":810.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":809.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So the trial campaign is going to last like all year long.","index":110,"end_time":814.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":811.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s not going to have the offer.","index":111,"end_time":815.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It''s just going to like be pushing people towards the club to, to come in and like try it out.","index":112,"end_time":820.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":815.8,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Then we''re going to be doing like separate campaigns with different offers and that kind of stuff.","index":113,"end_time":825.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":821.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then we''re going to do another.","index":114,"end_time":828.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":826.62,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Separate campaign hopefully with some group fitness content and that kind of stuff.","index":115,"end_time":833.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":828.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So it pushes people to the different like.","index":116,"end_time":835.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":833.14,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sectors of our, of our gyms.","index":117,"end_time":838.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.1,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That we want people to learn more about.","index":118,"end_time":840.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":838.94,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And, and what''s going to be the main so visual or video for the trial campaign?","index":119,"end_time":847.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":842.54,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Because now it''s, we have the forms and is it going to be just like a word campaign or.","index":120,"end_time":854.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":848.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"No, I have some of the videos.","index":121,"end_time":856,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":854.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And, and photos for the trial campaign.","index":122,"end_time":858.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":856,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That I''ll send over to you.","index":123,"end_time":859.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":858.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I want your team because this was done by the other marketing team and.","index":124,"end_time":863.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":859.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Their videos and, and ad sets have not been the, the best.","index":125,"end_time":868.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":863.84,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I want them to review it.","index":126,"end_time":870.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":869.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If it doesn''t I, if they want to make changes to it, please do and just send it over to me.","index":127,"end_time":878.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":870.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I can have a look at.","index":128,"end_time":879.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":878.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It but make the changes in order.","index":129,"end_time":882.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":879.95,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"For it to be the most efficient ad sets and ad videos possible.","index":130,"end_time":885.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":882.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But I''ll send all of that stuff.","index":131,"end_time":888.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.67,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Over to you now.","index":132,"end_time":888.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":888.07,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So we''ll do that for the campaigns for the trial campaign and then also the dollar down offer.","index":133,"end_time":897.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":888.91,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"The other marketing team should be sending.","index":134,"end_time":900.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":898.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That to me today as well so.","index":135,"end_time":904.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":900.72,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We can get that going.","index":136,"end_time":905.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":904.2,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you guys have.","index":137,"end_time":906.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Oh, excuse me, you guys have access to the Dropbox with all of our.","index":138,"end_time":914.839,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":907.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Old like photos and videos.","index":139,"end_time":916.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":914.839,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I would have to check Because I don''t think that I''ve ever.","index":140,"end_time":919.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":916.88,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Exit accident.","index":141,"end_time":920.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":919.28,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Yeah, you probably have.","index":142,"end_time":921.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":920.36,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":143,"end_time":923.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":922,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"But the lady before did and I know Colin probably saw it.","index":144,"end_time":927.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":923.28,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I will try and get, I''ll get that over to you guys as well.","index":145,"end_time":931.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":928.6,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And that way you guys have as much content as possible and you can just see what works best.","index":146,"end_time":936.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":931.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":147,"end_time":937.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":936.64,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay.","index":148,"end_time":938.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":937.8,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Do you need anything else from me on that?","index":149,"end_time":940.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":938.92,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"No, that''s all.","index":150,"end_time":942.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":941.4,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":151,"end_time":944.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.04,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So trial campaign dollar down offer being released on the 19th.","index":152,"end_time":950.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":944.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"We''re pausing the zoo enrollment the same day HubSpot Robert.","index":153,"end_time":957.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":950.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"HubSpot apparently is already synced to meta.","index":154,"end_time":961.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":957.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So they already communicate with each other which was on that call yesterday.","index":155,"end_time":965.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":961.46,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So I, I just want to learn how they communicate and like where we can see that kind of data.","index":156,"end_time":971.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":966.82,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"He is going to provide that some of that material and.","index":157,"end_time":977.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":972.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"SMS automation.","index":158,"end_time":981.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":980.34,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Robert, you still being approved by Trilio.","index":159,"end_time":987.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":982.44,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And HubSpot so they haven''t been able to complete that just yet.","index":160,"end_time":990.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":987.08,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"It says five to eight business days.","index":161,"end_time":992.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":991.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So hope.","index":162,"end_time":993.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":992.76,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I mean hopefully by.","index":163,"end_time":995,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":993.32,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And I did that about a week.","index":164,"end_time":996.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":995.24,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Ago so hopefully this week or, or next week that kind of stuff will be done.","index":165,"end_time":1001.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":996.4,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"If it starts on the 19th when.","index":166,"end_time":1004.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1002.68,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"The other campaigns also, that would be great.","index":167,"end_time":1007.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1004.52,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That would be great.","index":168,"end_time":1008.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1007.12,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"How about it?","index":169,"end_time":1009.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Close up.","index":170,"end_time":1010.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.74,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah, we need a win Nina.","index":171,"end_time":1012.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1011.3,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So let''s, let''s, let''s make it happen.","index":172,"end_time":1014.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1012.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":173,"end_time":1019.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1018.18,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Do you need more info from me on, on the meta ad stuff?","index":174,"end_time":1024.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Not yet.","index":175,"end_time":1026.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1025.86,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"If I need anything additional I will ask in the chat.","index":176,"end_time":1029.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.5,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So just to confirm Dropbox with old content, you need Dropbox with new content.","index":177,"end_time":1038.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Including the trial campaign material and the dollar down material.","index":178,"end_time":1049.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1039.16,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And that''s it.","index":179,"end_time":1053.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1052.68,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":180,"end_time":1054.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1054.04,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":181,"end_time":1059.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1055.48,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sounds good to me.","index":182,"end_time":1060.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1059.65,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And if you have anything else, ask in the channel.","index":183,"end_time":1066.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.01,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":184,"end_time":1068.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1067.49,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"In terms of the website, like invisible pages for the trial campaigns, you need anything from us there or you guys.","index":185,"end_time":1075.889,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1068.53,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Just have to do it?","index":186,"end_time":1076.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1075.889,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I think that our developers can do it because we have access from when we were fixing the site in Squarespace so we should be fine.","index":187,"end_time":1085.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1077.73,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay, cool, cool.","index":188,"end_time":1086.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1085.5,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"And then in terms of like all of our old campaigns and things like.","index":189,"end_time":1090.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.26,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"That, I''m assuming your team is going.","index":190,"end_time":1093.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1090.9,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"To like review it and then change all that stuff or how''s that going to work?","index":191,"end_time":1097.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1093.38,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Are they going to review it then send us the information on what they want to do and then we approve it.","index":192,"end_time":1102.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1097.66,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"So for, I mean if we have only the two campaigns running, so the trial campaign and the new dollar down campaign, those would be set by us.","index":193,"end_time":1111.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.34,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"So I mean this should be set.","index":194,"end_time":1113.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1111.62,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":195,"end_time":1114.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1113.95,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"For the one that we are shutting down.","index":196,"end_time":1115.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1114.43,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"I mean if we''re shutting it down, then I don''t think there''s really a need to review it.","index":197,"end_time":1119.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1115.99,"speaker_name":"Nina Belina"},{"text":"Okay.","index":198,"end_time":1121.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1120.39,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":199,"end_time":1121.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1121.03,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"All right.","index":200,"end_time":1122.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":201,"end_time":1123.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1122.63,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Robert, do you have anything else for Nina?","index":202,"end_time":1125.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1123.75,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":203,"end_time":1126.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1126.31,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''m good.","index":204,"end_time":1127.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.27,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Cool.","index":205,"end_time":1129.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1128.79,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Good stuff.","index":206,"end_time":1129.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1129.19,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Sounds like we''ve got some work to do.","index":207,"end_time":1131.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1130.55,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"I''ll get you that stuff as soon as possible, Nina.","index":208,"end_time":1133.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1131.99,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"},{"text":"Okay, thank you, thank you, thank you.","index":209,"end_time":1137.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1134.47,"speaker_name":"Milan Wagner"}],"dateString":"2026-01-14T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86061042503?pwd=x0TBEgRs7qFmrRIEItauCzbH71kaq8.1","participants":["yefei@yhatinvest.com,alex.white@yhatinvest.com,tatiana@powerhousegymsoflo.com,wyattc@yhatinvest.com,rober