e needed to replace that.","index":178,"end_time":453.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":449.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like I said, it''s updated in the header and footer with the copyright symbol.","index":179,"end_time":457.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":453.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"While it looks like.","index":180,"end_time":459.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":458.95,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Did you update the one that you just scrolled past right in the middle.","index":181,"end_time":462.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":459.83,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Of the page there?","index":182,"end_time":462.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yes.","index":183,"end_time":463.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":462.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":184,"end_time":464.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":463.75,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":185,"end_time":465.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I can look for some other instances.","index":186,"end_time":468.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.83,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But yeah, it''s.","index":187,"end_time":469.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":468.15,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":188,"end_time":470.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":470.61,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"As long as we''re displaying the registered logo, I think we''re probably good.","index":189,"end_time":474.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":470.89,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, this isn''t a big deal.","index":190,"end_time":475.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":474.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, if I don''t want to spend a lot of time on it.","index":191,"end_time":478.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":475.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So, you know, as we run across them.","index":192,"end_time":479.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":478.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If we run across them, we''ll fix them.","index":193,"end_time":481.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":479.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":194,"end_time":482.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":481.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let''s not put a lot of time on it.","index":195,"end_time":483.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":482.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, and then.","index":196,"end_time":485.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":483.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So MSP search campaign is live.","index":197,"end_time":487.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":485.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have that budget at $20 a day.","index":198,"end_time":490.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":487.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The Microsoft campaign is live as well, and that''s at $25 a day.","index":199,"end_time":492.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":490.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When I brought that up last week, he said he wanted to get back to me on those numbers.","index":200,"end_time":496.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":492.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re adjusting those as we see fit.","index":201,"end_time":499.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":202,"end_time":500.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":499.88,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know, we''re feeling like the price offer PMAX campaign is something we probably are going to either shrink or discontinue.","index":203,"end_time":508.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":501.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That has been a dud.","index":204,"end_time":510.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":205,"end_time":511.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":510.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We''ve gotten one opportunity off of that and it was very recent.","index":206,"end_time":514.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.559,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And it doesn''t look like Chris has been able to get ahold of them.","index":207,"end_time":516.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Chris?","index":208,"end_time":517.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.76,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah, it was this week.","index":209,"end_time":518.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":517.12,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":210,"end_time":518.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":518.24,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You muted.","index":211,"end_time":520.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":519.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''m sorry, which one?","index":212,"end_time":521.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.6,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"The Penn State guy or the university?","index":213,"end_time":524.389,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":522.229,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Pennsylvania guy.","index":214,"end_time":525.829,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":524.869,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I don''t think he''s.","index":215,"end_time":527.509,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.469,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I don''t think he actually works at Penn State anymore.","index":216,"end_time":530.229,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":527.669,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"He''s.","index":217,"end_time":531.269,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":530.789,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"These guys get these college email addresses and they.","index":218,"end_time":534.149,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.509,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"You can use them for personal.","index":219,"end_time":535.589,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":534.549,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Whatever use them for.","index":220,"end_time":536.789,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":535.669,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah, but I sent him an email, but it didn''t.","index":221,"end_time":540.789,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":537.829,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"And it didn''t bounce.","index":222,"end_time":541.829,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":540.789,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"So.","index":223,"end_time":542.229,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.829,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been on that.","index":224,"end_time":545.149,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":543.749,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"And I mean, it didn''t.","index":225,"end_time":546.629,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":545.149,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I haven''t got a response yet.","index":226,"end_time":548.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":547.6,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Okay, well, that''s the only app we''ve gotten on that one, so we''re probably gonna slowly try to phase that one out.","index":227,"end_time":554,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":549.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":228,"end_time":554.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":554.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":229,"end_time":555.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":555.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, well, I''m all yours then for any other updates from your guys.","index":230,"end_time":559.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":556.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Side.","index":231,"end_time":559.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":559.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, are you done?","index":232,"end_time":563.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":562.56,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that everything you had for us, Colin?","index":233,"end_time":565.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":563.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":234,"end_time":565.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":235,"end_time":566.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":565.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we are going to do.","index":236,"end_time":568.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I want to do a Ringcentral.","index":237,"end_time":573,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":571.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''ve gotten quite a few articles on Ringcentral.","index":238,"end_time":575.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I want to do a ring central landing page.","index":239,"end_time":577.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":575.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":240,"end_time":578.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":578.07,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Now the problem is how do we get people to it?","index":241,"end_time":582.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Because we can''t search the terms.","index":242,"end_time":583.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":582.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The terms seem to be nothing, you know, that you can get on.","index":243,"end_time":587.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":583.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So how do we get.","index":244,"end_time":588.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":587.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If we create this page, how do we get people to this page?","index":245,"end_time":591.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":588.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Now the way we could do it is we can do it through email.","index":246,"end_time":594.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":591.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":247,"end_time":595.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":595.03,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We can do our emails to people we think have Ringcentral.","index":248,"end_time":597.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":595.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We can do it through our blog posts.","index":249,"end_time":599.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":597.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"People who are Searching up ringcentral stuff.","index":250,"end_time":602.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":600.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But is there a campaign we can put together in Google that would get us people there?","index":251,"end_time":607.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which, based on what little knowledge I have, it doesn''t appear there is because it doesn''t.","index":252,"end_time":611.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":607.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like Ringcentral terms don''t seem to be anything with any volume that we can get on.","index":253,"end_time":615.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":611.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do we agree with that?","index":254,"end_time":616.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":615.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":255,"end_time":617.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":617.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, for the ones that we''ve been trying to fight to get even market share of, they fight back.","index":256,"end_time":622.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":617.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other question is, you know, how we can''t.","index":257,"end_time":626.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":624.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like ring central replacement isn''t like a searchable term on Google.","index":258,"end_time":630.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":626.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like no one searches it.","index":259,"end_time":631.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":630.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is it on in Microsoft too?","index":260,"end_time":634.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Not as far as I know.","index":261,"end_time":637.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":636.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, my question would be like, if you go Ringcentral replacement, low search volume, bullshit, you get on Google, on Google, is that the same on Microsoft?","index":262,"end_time":650.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you still get that same bullshit?","index":263,"end_time":651.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I have to check into that for you.","index":264,"end_time":653.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":652.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":265,"end_time":654.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Could you.","index":266,"end_time":654.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":267,"end_time":655.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":655.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Look into those terms that we, you know, we want to get on that.","index":268,"end_time":659.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Google''s basically saying, no, you can''t because there''s no value amount, which we know there is.","index":269,"end_time":663.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":659.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":270,"end_time":664.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":664.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we create these custom landing pages, we probably aren''t going to be able to get on.","index":271,"end_time":669.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":665.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re probably not going to be able to get it in a Google campaign.","index":272,"end_time":673.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":670.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re likely going to have to drive through email and blog.","index":273,"end_time":676.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that what we''re thinking?","index":274,"end_time":677.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":676.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"SEO.","index":275,"end_time":679.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":678.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Correct.","index":276,"end_time":679.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":679.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, agreed.","index":277,"end_time":681.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":679.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, you know, something that could be of use soon as they''re rolling it out, is chatgpt is slowly enabling ads.","index":278,"end_time":688.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":681.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So as more information comes out about that, I''m trying to say very plugged in.","index":279,"end_time":692.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":688.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sam Altman said that was a very last resort is what he said years ago, to do ads.","index":280,"end_time":698.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":693.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"His company''s not turning a profit, so now he''s like, do a. Yeah, I.","index":281,"end_time":706.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":701.17,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Mean, you got to do something.","index":282,"end_time":707.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":706.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":283,"end_time":708.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":708.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, there''s no reason they can''t do ads.","index":284,"end_time":710.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":708.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s fine.","index":285,"end_time":710.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s not, you know, it''s just a matter of time till you can buy influence.","index":286,"end_time":713.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''ll be where it all goes to shit.","index":287,"end_time":716.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":714.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":288,"end_time":717.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":717.1,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"I mean, Reddit did it with Google.","index":289,"end_time":719.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":718.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s why Google''s been in a lawsuit for like almost two years.","index":290,"end_time":722.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":719.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":291,"end_time":723.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Did I ever tell you guys that crazy metric Reddit had a post and like within 45 minutes it was number one on Google?","index":292,"end_time":730.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":725.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":293,"end_time":731.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":294,"end_time":731.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":731.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":295,"end_time":731.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":731.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You told us that.","index":296,"end_time":732.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Insane.","index":297,"end_time":733.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":732.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":298,"end_time":735.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":734.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think those are going to be the main channels of driving traffic there.","index":299,"end_time":737.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":735.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''ll do some keyword research and then I''ll also check into the Microsoft Thing and see if how the RingCentral replacement search works there.","index":300,"end_time":743.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":738.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":301,"end_time":745.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":745.27,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"While we''re on that.","index":302,"end_time":748.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":747.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So what we''re building, we''re close.","index":303,"end_time":751.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":748.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do we want to go talk about this now, Lindsey?","index":304,"end_time":753.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":752.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":305,"end_time":754.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":753.99,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So we''re pretty close on this.","index":306,"end_time":757.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":756.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So let me share for a second.","index":307,"end_time":758.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":757.35,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let me share the latest version just to see.","index":308,"end_time":761.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":759.03,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, here we go.","index":309,"end_time":763.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":762.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, let me share my screen.","index":310,"end_time":765.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":763.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So what I''m going to do is build these out, Colin.","index":311,"end_time":768.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":766.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And we''re going to do multiples of these.","index":312,"end_time":770.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":768.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like my next one.","index":313,"end_time":774.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":773.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"This first one we''re going to do is like Ringcentral.","index":314,"end_time":775.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Second one is going to be like Comcast.","index":315,"end_time":777.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":775.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re just going to build these out to these pages.","index":316,"end_time":778.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":777.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So they''re basically quizzes and don''t spend a lot of time on what the questions are.","index":317,"end_time":783.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":779.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re just.","index":318,"end_time":783.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.51,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m kind of still working through it.","index":319,"end_time":785.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So are you currently using RingCentral?","index":320,"end_time":788.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.51,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yes.","index":321,"end_time":788.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":788.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"When did you sign your contract?","index":322,"end_time":790.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":789.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How many users?","index":323,"end_time":793.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What are you paying per seat?","index":324,"end_time":795.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":793.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Watch.","index":325,"end_time":800.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":800.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What issues are you experiencing?","index":326,"end_time":802.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":800.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s basically a cost calculator, but it''s very specific to rig central to whoever it''s going to be.","index":327,"end_time":808.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":802.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":328,"end_time":809.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":808.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I build it.","index":329,"end_time":810.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":809.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Mostly I build it all on Claude.","index":330,"end_time":812.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":810.62,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Don''t you love cloud code?","index":331,"end_time":814.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":813.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This was very impressive.","index":332,"end_time":816.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":814.98,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I was blown away by.","index":333,"end_time":818.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":816.3,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Right.","index":334,"end_time":819.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":818.74,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So then we get this thing.","index":335,"end_time":820.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re a strong fit, blah, blah, blah.","index":336,"end_time":822.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Here''s all your stuff, what you''ll get with Tech mode and then it goes into this.","index":337,"end_time":827.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":822.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So let''s just fill it out.","index":338,"end_time":829.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":827.9,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And this is.","index":339,"end_time":829.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":829.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m going to need you here for a second on this.","index":340,"end_time":831.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":829.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Once I get this thing working, it''s easy for me just to change the questions for whoever it''s going to be.","index":341,"end_time":843.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":838.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Schedule your free consult.","index":342,"end_time":845.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":844.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Off it goes from here.","index":343,"end_time":849.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s going to.","index":344,"end_time":849.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":849.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Where''s it going, Lindsey?","index":345,"end_time":852.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":851.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s going to Gravity forms.","index":346,"end_time":854.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":852.18,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"In our WordPress, we enabled the REST API and we were able to get it connected and it is accepting submissions, but we cannot get it to then notify us that a submission has been made.","index":347,"end_time":869.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":855.54,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I have changed the submission email.","index":348,"end_time":871.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":869.54,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''ve done several things to try to get it to notify me that a submission has come through, but it just won''t do it.","index":349,"end_time":879.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":871.3,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But it shows.","index":350,"end_time":881.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.85,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We''ve tested it four times.","index":351,"end_time":882.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":881.29,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Inside of Gravity Forms, it''s showing four submissions with all the correct information.","index":352,"end_time":886.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":882.65,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So how do I get it to send me an email?","index":353,"end_time":890.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":888.17,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, let me log into the site.","index":354,"end_time":894.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":892.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":355,"end_time":895.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_tim