_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Matt, can you try filling that out again?","index":397,"end_time":1012.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1010.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep, I can.","index":398,"end_time":1014.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So you can just put in test information, because none of this stuff is validating right now.","index":399,"end_time":1023.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1019.33,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We just put it as, you know, accept any information to try to get it to work.","index":400,"end_time":1028.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1023.97,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Sam.","index":401,"end_time":1061.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.9,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Done.","index":402,"end_time":1061.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1061.59,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":403,"end_time":1085.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1084.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":404,"end_time":1087.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1087.04,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, sorry.","index":405,"end_time":1089.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1088.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was just testing to see if it would come through to me, but it''s not.","index":406,"end_time":1091.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1089.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I gotta dive in deeper to this.","index":407,"end_time":1092.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1091.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":408,"end_time":1097.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Does it look.","index":409,"end_time":1098.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1097.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which I don''t.","index":410,"end_time":1098.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1098.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You guys have to, like, look at the.","index":