ur other forms where they create.","index":425,"end_time":1126.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1121.25,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Create a contact in HubSpot and then it notifies us that way.","index":426,"end_time":1131.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1127.25,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Of course, we did not even attempt to get into any of the HubSpot stuff.","index":427,"end_time":1134.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1131.05,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":428,"end_time":1138.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1137.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can.","index":429,"end_time":1138.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can do the HubSpot side too, when I check into.","index":430,"end_time":1140.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1138.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"First of all, why this isn''t going to.","index":431,"end_time":1143.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1141.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And sending a notification.","index":432,"end_time":1144.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1143.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But if we could find a way to, like, you know, once we get this working, if we could figure out a way to like, duplicate this quickly so we could do this for multiple providers, that would be the ultimate goal.","index":433,"end_time":1157.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1147.16,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t know why we wouldn''t just use the same.","index":434,"end_time":1159.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1157.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We could just send it to the same form.","index":435,"end_time":1161.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1159.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The answers are going to be different, right?","index":436,"end_time":1162.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The answers are going to be different, but if you use the same form, it''s going to be titled the same.","index":437,"end_time":1167.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1163.16,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So each submission will say it''s the ringcentral cost savings, whatever.","index":438,"end_time":1171.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1167.52,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Oh, fair enough.","index":439,"end_time":1173.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1172.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know what I''m saying?","index":440,"end_time":1173.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1173.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yes, but I don''t want to have to duplicate all that code again.","index":441,"end_time":1177.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1174.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Man, you''re officially a marketer.","index":442,"end_time":1182.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.61,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Look at you go.","index":443,"end_time":1183.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1182.29,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, might be able to build.","index":444,"end_time":1184.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1183.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"He''s officially a coder now.","index":445,"end_time":1187.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1185.89,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And I''ve got troubles with the code.","index":446,"end_time":1188.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1187.13,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Ryan, you have no idea how many times I''m like, in there changing it and asking it to do stuff, and then I''m like, I get it so hung up and destroyed.","index":447,"end_time":1198.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1191.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I just have to reset and go back to the base.","index":448,"end_time":1201.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1198.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The base.","index":449,"end_time":1202.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1201.86,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"On it.","index":450,"end_time":1205.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1204.66,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":451,"end_time":1206.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1205.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Basically like.","index":452,"end_time":1207.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1206.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":453,"end_time":1208.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1207.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And Claude doesn''t like to forget.","index":454,"end_time":1211.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So you have to actually go in.","index":455,"end_time":1212.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And be like, you gotta forget this.","index":456,"end_time":1214.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1212.3,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Delete the whole conversation that we just had.","index":457,"end_time":1216.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1214.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Erase your memory.","index":458,"end_time":1217.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1216.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like the.","index":459,"end_time":1218.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1217.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What do you want it like the Men in Black.","index":460,"end_time":1220.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1218.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We had a Men in Blacket.","index":461,"end_time":1222.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1221.14,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":462,"end_time":1223.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1222.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":463,"end_time":1223.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1223.14,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I gotta put my glasses on.","index":464,"end_time":1224.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1223.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":465,"end_time":1226.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1226.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So the thought is Colin on these.","index":466,"end_time":1231.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1229.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re gonna do a ring, we''re gonna do a comcast.","index":467,"end_time":1234.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1231.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re gonna duplicate this cost savings calculator onto the page and then we''ll incorporate that into our blogs.","index":468,"end_time":1241.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1234.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re just gonna keep building that out.","index":469,"end_time":1242.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1241.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":470,"end_time":1243.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1242.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My thought.","index":471,"end_time":1243.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1243.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m wondering though, with.","index":472,"end_time":1245.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1244.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you like.","index":473,"end_time":1246.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1245.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you love.","index":474,"end_time":1246.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1246.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you love.","index":475,"end_time":1247.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1247.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you like or do you hate this idea?","index":476,"end_time":1250.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1248.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t hate it, Matt.","index":477,"end_time":1251.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1250.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s good.","index":478,"end_time":1252.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1252.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s good.","index":479,"end_time":1252.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1252.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s a good start.","index":480,"end_time":1253.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1252.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But I''m wondering if you could use one form and just have a placeholder in The Claude code for like page title where like we could just have.","index":481,"end_time":1262.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1254.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It and then do that.","index":482,"end_time":1263.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1262.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That way you don''t have to duplicate it.","index":483,"end_time":1265.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1264.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Lindsay and Gravity forms.","index":484,"end_time":1267.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1265.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can just have form title, like be dynamic.","index":485,"end_time":1269.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1267.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, that would be cool.","index":486,"end_time":1271.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1270.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, we could do that.","index":487,"end_time":1272.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1271.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We absolutely could do that.","index":488,"end_time":1273.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1272.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That would save you a lot of time for sure.","index":489,"end_time":1275.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1273.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":490,"end_time":1276.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1276.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll dig in.","index":491,"end_time":1277.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1276.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This notification thing is pissed me off because all the settings are correct.","index":492,"end_time":1280.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1277.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Look at that.","index":493,"end_time":1282.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1282.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Lindsay.","index":494,"end_time":1283.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1282.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It wasn''t us.","index":495,"end_time":1283.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1283.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yay.","index":496,"end_time":1284.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1283.85,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I thought they were all correct too.","index":497,"end_time":1286.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1284.97,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I just couldn''t quite figure out what the problem was.","index":498,"end_time":1288.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1286.33,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, so.","index":499,"end_time":1291.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1290.17,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But seriously, back to the idea of building these out and then we advertise on ones.","index":500,"end_time":1296.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1292.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We can.","index":501,"end_time":1297.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1296.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We, you know, like, I think.","index":502,"end_time":1298.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How many like Ringcentral.","index":503,"end_time":1299.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1298.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How many blogs do we have now?","index":504,"end_time":1300.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1299.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like four or five.","index":505,"end_time":1301.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1300.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Six or seven.","index":506,"end_time":1302.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1302.09,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Six or seven.","index":507,"end_time":1304.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1303.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we just kind of.","index":508,"end_time":1307.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1306.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Then we do some email campaigns.","index":509,"end_time":1308.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1307.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We keep coming all back.","index":510,"end_time":1310.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1308.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Excuse me.","index":511,"end_time":1311.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1310.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We keep coming back to this homepage where we have information on our blogs, we have information on this tool.","index":512,"end_time":1317.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1311.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, we just keep building that out to try to.","index":513,"end_time":1319.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1317.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":514,"end_time":1320.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1320.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Keep adding steps to their, you know, if they''re still doing informational search or you know, give them somewhere to go, whether they''re at step one or step five in the funnel.","index":515,"end_time":1329.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1320.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, agreed.","index":516,"end_time":1330.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1329.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s our thought.","index":517,"end_time":1332.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1331.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep, that''s exactly spot on.","index":518,"end_time":1335.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1332.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":519,"end_time":1336.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1335.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was there anything else from your guys side?","index":520,"end_time":1341.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1340.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lindsey probably had a few more things in there too.","index":521,"end_time":1344.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1342.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let me, let me, let me look, let me look.","index":522,"end_time":1346.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1344.77,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Let me look.","index":523,"end_time":1346.969,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1346.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay, so Ringcentral landing page we talked about.","index":524,"end_time":1349.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1346.969,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"SMB page we talked about.","index":525,"end_time":1352.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1350.33,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"See here.","index":526,"end_time":1357.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1357.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Was there any further discussion to be had about the AI readiness of the site?","index":527,"end_time":1369.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1363.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Sorry, you cut out for a second there.","index":528,"end_time":1372.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1370.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What was that?","index":529,"end_time":1372.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1372.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I said was there any more discussion to be had about AI readiness of our website and things that we can do going forward?","index":530,"end_time":1380.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1372.98,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Oh, and also we wanted to discuss creating some different blog post layouts, some different blog post templates, and then I think also potentially some image generation as well so that we can start having our blogs not all look exactly the same.","index":531,"end_time":1399.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1380.66,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You know, the table of contents is great, but right now, you know, all the blogs are just straight in line and we''re not putting any images in there.","index":532,"end_time":1407.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1399.92,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So if you have a recommendation for a product that I should start to use to.","index":533,"end_time":1413.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1407.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"For image generation, I think that would be helpful.","index":534,"end_time":1417.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1414.06,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":535,"end_time":1418.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1418.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Wasn''t it Banana Rama.","index":536,"end_time":1419.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1418.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Banana.","index":537,"end_time":1420.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1420.14,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Nano.","index":538,"end_time":1423.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Banana.","index":539,"end_time":1424.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1423.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nano.","index":540,"end_time":1424.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1424.3,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Banana.","index":541,"end_time":1425.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1424.94,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"All right, I''ll check that out.","index":542,"end_time":1426.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1425.58,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But we use Mid Journey to generate our photos.","index":543,"end_time":1434.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1429.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is there a cost difference or like, why did you guys choose that product over the other one.","index":544,"end_time":1442.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1436.79,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s just been the strongest, like, as far as results.","index":545,"end_time":1445.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1442.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s.","index":546,"end_time":1446.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1445.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re not getting like all the people with like five hands and all sorts of stuff like that.","index":547,"end_time":1451.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1446.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a really easy, like, prompting process.","index":548,"end_time":1453.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1451.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The generations are pretty quick.","index":549,"end_time":1456.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1454.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s usually like they''ll give you four options in less than a minute.","index":550,"end_time":1459.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1456.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You do video less than a minute.","index":551,"end_time":1462.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1461.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s pretty good.","index":552,"end_time":1463.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1462.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":553,"end_time":1464.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1463.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can do video creation, all sorts of stuff.","index":554,"end_time":1468.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1464.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think they handle their billing through.","index":555,"end_time":1472.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1470.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know we at least log in through Discord, but they may have changed that since we set up our account.","index":556,"end_time":1476.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1472.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Billings through Discord.","index":557,"end_time":1481.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1478.93,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":558,"end_time":1482.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1481.41,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Going through Gabe.","index":559,"end_time":1484.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1482.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, Gabe doesn''t know in Discord.","index":560,"end_time":1486.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1485.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s got Steam.","index":561,"end_time":1487.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1486.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"But yeah, can definitely come up with an updated blog post template.","index":562,"end_time":1494.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1491.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Couple of them.","index":563,"end_time":1496.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":564,"end_time":1498.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1497.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I think if we could have three templates to choose from for blog posts, I think that would be.","index":565,"end_time":1503.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1498.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And I''ll just check with the developers, but I''m pretty sure with a post type, we''re limited.","index":566,"end_time":1510.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1504.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll see what we can do.","index":567,"end_time":1513.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1511.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We might be able to come up with like a new post type to utilize where we can have multiple templates based on like a resource type or something.","index":568,"end_time":1519.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1513.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But I''ll see what we can do there.","index":569,"end_time":1520.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1519.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":570,"end_time":1521.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1521.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Let''s make it Cthulhu style.","index":571,"end_time":1532.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1530.47,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Let''s go all like straight up medieval.","index":572,"end_time":1536.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1532.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''ll start writing my blogs in like medieval speak, like hear ye and we''ll.","index":573,"end_time":1544.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1539.99,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Get you set up in less than a fortnight.","index":574,"end_time":1546.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1544.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s.","index":575,"end_time":1550.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1547.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s Taylor.","index":576,"end_time":1551.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1550.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Taylor owns that term now, Colin.","index":577,"end_time":1553.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1551.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You can''t say it without having to pay tribute to Taylor.","index":578,"end_time":1557.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1553.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"She''s copywritten that term.","index":579,"end_time":1559,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1557.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Who''s Taylor?","index":580,"end_time":1560.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1559.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Taylor Swift.","index":581,"end_time":1561.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1561,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, God.","index":582,"end_time":1563.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1562.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You didn''t know Matt was a Swifty.","index":583,"end_time":1567.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1565.8,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I did not.","index":584,"end_time":1568.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1567.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now you don''t.","index":585,"end_time":1569.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1568.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Matt assumes Everybody''s at least 75.","index":586,"end_time":1571.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1569.56,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"The same amount of fandom as he.","index":587,"end_time":1573.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1571.96,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Is on Taylor Swift.","index":588,"end_time":1574.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1573.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I think, yeah, we''re on a.","index":589,"end_time":1576.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1574.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"First name basis with her, but she doesn''t know us.","index":590,"end_time":1578.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1576.19,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Tay Tay.","index":591,"end_time":1579.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1578.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I could have said Tay Tay.","index":592,"end_time":1580.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1579.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We actually used to have a member of the team that dated her brother for years.","index":593,"end_time":1585.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1581.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How about that?","index":594,"end_time":1588.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1587.51,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But apparently their family is nuts.","index":595,"end_time":1589.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1588.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, I mean, wouldn''t surprise me.","index":596,"end_time":1592.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1591.029,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, all of them, but Taylor.","index":597,"end_time":1596.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Taylor''s not nuts.","index":598,"end_time":1597.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1596.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Damn Rhode Islanders.","index":599,"end_time":1598.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1597.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And she''s look, I mean, she''s got a little something going on, I''m sure.","index":600,"end_time":1602.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1599.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"No doubt.","index":601,"end_time":1604.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1603.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Can''t have that many breakups and songs about them.","index":602,"end_time":1607.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1604.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":603,"end_time":1608.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1607.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You have to be a good.","index":604,"end_time":1609.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1608.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You have to like, you have to Be a little crazy to be a good songwriter.","index":605,"end_time":1612.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1609.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, for sure.","index":606,"end_time":1613.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1612.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Especially, like, a pop star like that.","index":607,"end_time":1615.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1613.54,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You don''t live on planet Earth ever.","index":608,"end_time":1616.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1615.22,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, she''s.","index":609,"end_time":1618.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1617.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"She''s wild, for sure.","index":610,"end_time":1619.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1618.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Travis, Kelsey.","index":611,"end_time":1621.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1620.34,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, all those guys, like, all the greatest song, like, generational songwriters of our time, like Allison Change.","index":612,"end_time":1629.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1624.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I can''t think of his name.","index":613,"end_time":1630.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1629.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And, yeah, all those guys, man, they were dark.","index":614,"end_time":1634.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1631.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Had all kinds of.","index":615,"end_time":1635.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1634.27,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah.","index":616,"end_time":1636.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1635.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Rooster.","index":617,"end_time":1636.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1636.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":618,"end_time":1636.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1636.67,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Some of those guys from that era were not even putting it on.","index":619,"end_time":1639.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1636.91,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It was dark.","index":620,"end_time":1640.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1639.79,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":621,"end_time":1642.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1641.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s.","index":622,"end_time":1642.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1642.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s highly.","index":623,"end_time":1643.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1642.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s like, it''s creative types and smarter people.","index":624,"end_time":1646.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1643.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Highly linked to, like, depression and things like that.","index":625,"end_time":1648.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1646.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, it''s what you tell stories from.","index":626,"end_time":1650.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1648.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I gotta give me some of that depression so I can pretend I''m smart.","index":627,"end_time":1655.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Think about, like, Mark Twain all you want, man.","index":628,"end_time":1658.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1656.03,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, you can take all.","index":629,"end_time":1660.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1658.51,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I''ll give you whatever you want for depression.","index":630,"end_time":1662.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1660.91,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You can.","index":631,"end_time":1662.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1662.63,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Can take it.","index":632,"end_time":1663.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1662.9,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":633,"end_time":1666.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1666.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The lows are low, and the highs are never that high.","index":634,"end_time":1670.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1667.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s the problem.","index":635,"end_time":1671.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1670.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":636,"end_time":1674.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1674.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that not it?","index":637,"end_time":1675.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1674.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No.","index":638,"end_time":1676.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.02,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We hit a high, we''re like, okay, that''s too much.","index":639,"end_time":1678.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1676.38,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You''re like, oh, I won the lottery.","index":640,"end_time":1679.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1678.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, that''s pretty nice.","index":641,"end_time":1680.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1679.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Or you hit a high and you''re like, exactly.","index":642,"end_time":1683.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1681.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Matt, what''s the next thing?","index":643,"end_time":1685.06,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1683.14,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You hit a high and you''re like, this isn''t as much as I expected.","index":644,"end_time":1688.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1685.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To enjoy it.","index":645,"end_time":1689.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1688.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":646,"end_time":1690.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1689.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Or instead of saying, I won the lottery, say, well, I think of all the taxes I got to pay now.","index":647,"end_time":1695.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1690.52,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":648,"end_time":1695.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1695.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just said, chris, that''s all my joke.","index":649,"end_time":1700.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1695.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right in front of me.","index":650,"end_time":1701.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1700.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We were talking to a family friend.","index":651,"end_time":1704.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1702.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Review.","index":652,"end_time":1704.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1704.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Somebody write that down.","index":653,"end_time":1705.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1704.48,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We were talking to a family friend, and at that point, the lottery was like, almost $1 billion.","index":654,"end_time":1711.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1707.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was a few months ago.","index":655,"end_time":1712.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1711.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And he was like, yeah, but, you know, after taxes, you''re only taking home, like, 500 million, 600 million.","index":656,"end_time":1717.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1713,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m like, I would still love that.","index":657,"end_time":1718.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1717.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Five or six hundred million dollars.","index":658,"end_time":1720.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1718.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"My bank account.","index":659,"end_time":1721.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1720.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a good problem.","index":660,"end_time":1722.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1721.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":661,"end_time":1723.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1722.74,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"What''s funny about that is somebody said on that lottery, like, if you win, that you''re a billionaire, but you''re not taxed like a billionaire.","index":662,"end_time":1732.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1723.78,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re taxed like a common person.","index":663,"end_time":1733.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1732.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s like, why can''t we tax billionaires like we tax billionaire lottery winners.","index":664,"end_time":1738.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1734.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I''m like, you know what?","index":665,"end_time":1739.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1738.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s an excellent point.","index":666,"end_time":1740.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1739.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":667,"end_time":1740.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1740.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that it''s like you get taxed like a chump on that.","index":668,"end_time":1744.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1740.7,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":669,"end_time":1744.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1744.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not like a regular person.","index":670,"end_time":1747.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1746.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":671,"end_time":1748.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1748.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":672,"end_time":1749.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1748.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Which is ironic.","index":673,"end_time":1752.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1751.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That makes it even More depressing, right?","index":674,"end_time":1755.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1752.8,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":675,"end_time":1759.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1759.28,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Welcome to the club, Brian.","index":676,"end_time":1761.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1759.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like in Star wars, though, you sit on the council, we do not grant you the rank of master.","index":677,"end_time":1767.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1761.88,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":678,"end_time":1768.32,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1767.44,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"No, you''re a billionaire.","index":679,"end_time":1769.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.32,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We don''t grant you the benefits of being a billionaire.","index":680,"end_time":1771.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1769.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, no.","index":681,"end_time":1773.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1772.56,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"All right, I don''t.","index":682,"end_time":1778.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1777.56,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What else do we have?","index":683,"end_time":1779.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1778.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Lindsay, I think that was it.","index":684,"end_time":1780.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.04,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s what I''m.","index":685,"end_time":1781.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1780.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s what I''ve got to discuss.","index":686,"end_time":1783,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1781.56,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"The log templates, the form we just went through, and then finding out of Ringcentral has locked us out of Bing terms as well.","index":687,"end_time":1794.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.32,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''ll check into that.","index":688,"end_time":1796.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1795.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then also this notification issue.","index":689,"end_time":1797.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1796.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":690,"end_time":1799.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1798.84,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"On those forms, are we.","index":691,"end_time":1801,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1799.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is everything working on the Bing form?","index":692,"end_time":1804.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1802.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If somebody goes and do we have a landing page for that or we redoing the SMB page for that?","index":693,"end_time":1808.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1804.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":694,"end_time":1809.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1808.79,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is that our plan for the Microsoft ads?","index":695,"end_time":1811.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1809.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes, that was the landing page that we developed before the SMB page.","index":696,"end_time":1814.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1811.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Got it.","index":697,"end_time":1815.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1815.15,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Okay.","index":698,"end_time":1816.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1815.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And we sure the form works on that?","index":699,"end_time":1817.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1816.03,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we tested it.","index":700,"end_time":1819.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1818.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":701,"end_time":1820.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1819.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, I''ll dig in.","index":702,"end_time":1823.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1822.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So far we''ve had one click on that ad, no form fill outs.","index":703,"end_time":1829.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1824.43,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"All right.","index":704,"end_time":1832.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1832.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, it was a.","index":705,"end_time":1835.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1834.44,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s a shot.","index":706,"end_time":1836.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1835.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Not guess.","index":707,"end_time":1836.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1836.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It doesn''t have to work.","index":708,"end_time":1837.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1836.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It doesn''t cost us anything unless they click right.","index":709,"end_time":1839.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1837.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s correct.","index":710,"end_time":1840.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1839.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s correct.","index":711,"end_time":1842.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1841.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":712,"end_time":1845.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1844.52,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So far it has cost us 5 cents.","index":713,"end_time":1849.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1845.12,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Effective thing this team''s ever done, playing.","index":714,"end_time":1856.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1854.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"In a much less crowded sandbox for your competitors.","index":715,"end_time":1860.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1856.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, well, we know.","index":716,"end_time":1863.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1862.05,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We know a few people on our team who search in Bing.","index":717,"end_time":1866.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1863.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think I finally scared him off of it.","index":718,"end_time":1869.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1867.89,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Now it''s not just.","index":719,"end_time":1872.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1871.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s not just him.","index":720,"end_time":1873.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1872.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"There''s others.","index":721,"end_time":1874.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1873.89,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Lindsay.","index":722,"end_time":1875.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1874.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Ghostal thing.","index":723,"end_time":1878.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1877.17,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"What''s that?","index":724,"end_time":1879.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1878.8,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Is DuckDuckGo still a thing?","index":725,"end_time":1881.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1880,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"DuckDuckGo.","index":726,"end_time":1882.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1881.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, brave.","index":727,"end_time":1883.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1882.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, there''s a few of those.","index":728,"end_time":1884.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1883.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But supposedly that doesn''t have the liberal slant that the.","index":729,"end_time":1890.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1887.44,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"That reality does.","index":730,"end_time":1891.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1890.6,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"DuckDuckGo markets itself as more like.","index":731,"end_time":1894.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1892.24,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Like a private.","index":732,"end_time":1896.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1895.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, a private browser.","index":733,"end_time":1898.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1897.2,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":734,"end_time":1899.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1899.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s Brave''s thing too.","index":735,"end_time":1900.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1899.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So their whole thing is like, we don''t do advertising because everyone''s private.","index":736,"end_time":1904.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1901.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You shouldn''t know who they are.","index":737,"end_time":1905.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1904.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s all great until my TV is watching me and every keystroke I make.","index":738,"end_time":1910.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1907.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yep.","index":739,"end_time":1911.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1911.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So.","index":740,"end_time":1912.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1912.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And Alexa sitting right.","index":741,"end_time":1914.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1913.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Alexa''s listening.","index":742,"end_time":1915.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1914.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was just gonna say right next.","index":743,"end_time":1916.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1915.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To me, like, I couldn''t have her any closer.","index":744,"end_time":1918.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1916.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":745,"end_time":1919.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1918.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Have her transcribe the calls.","index":746,"end_time":1923.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1921.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No doubt.","index":747,"end_time":1924.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1923.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":748,"end_time":1926.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1925.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"All right, well, we''ll hop on this stuff and then I''ll show.","index":749,"end_time":1929.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1926.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s working.","index":750,"end_time":1929.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1929.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, go there when you think.","index":751,"end_time":1930.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1929.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you need me to test it, let me know.","index":752,"end_time":1932.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1930.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Will do.","index":753,"end_time":1932.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1932.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":754,"end_time":1933.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1933.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Thank you guys for your time.","index":755,"end_time":1934.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1933.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":756,"end_time":1935.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1934.76,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":757,"end_time":1936.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1935.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Bye.","index":758,"end_time":1936.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1936.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"}],"dateString":"2026-01-20T20:00:00.000Z","host_email":"lhall@techmode.com","meeting_link":"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_ODBmZWFjMWYtMWIxYi00NmZmLTgyMDEtOWFiZWJhYWEwYzVh@thread.v2/0?context={\"Tid\":\"3801011d-e732-48ee-be2a-e499b1a29ba4\",\"Oid\":\"e804fbe9-a623-4d26-a887-992e62fb92d1\"}","participants":["cquigley@techmode.com,michael.lewis@techmode.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,lhall@techmode.com,mlook@techmode.com,rfisher@techmode.com","cquigley@techmode.com","michael.lewis@techmode.com","colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","mlook@techmode.com","rfisher@techmode.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KF9M61EM3G63FDFH1NSYAFM5","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Confirmed payment issues were resolved; Colin validated invoice was sent and processed.","Aligned on SMB landing page emphasizing value without enterprise language; new copy approved.","Approved cost calculator tool tied to provider; Gravity Forms integration troubleshooting underway.","Agreed to retire underperforming PMAX campaign; search and Microsoft campaigns remain active.","Planned dynamic landing pages and quizzes for competitors like Ringcentral and Comcast."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Our close rate is actually pretty freaking good.","speaker":"Matthew Look"},{"quote":"We just paid you guys. It''s paid. So perfect.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"We''re going to do a Ringcentral landing page.","speaker":"Matthew Look"}],"topics":["delivery","campaign","tooling","scope"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-20T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **SMB Landing Page and Campaign Strategy**\n\nThe team decided to create a dedicated **SMB landing page** emphasizing personalized, enterprise-level support for small to mid-sized businesses, avoiding terms like \"Enterprise\" to prevent misinterpretation (05:18).\n\n- **Matthew Look confirmed** the close rate is strong but drops significantly after **70+ seats**, highlighting the need to focus on SMBs with fewer users (05:45).\n    - They adjusted user ranges to **5 to 100 seats** to better target SMBs.\n    - The landing page will emphasize \"one call for all your needs\" with **live answer support**, appealing to SMBs seeking hassle-free service post-sale.\n    - Testimonials will be integrated from the homepage to build trust.\n    - This approach aims to differentiate from competitors who treat SMBs impersonally.\n\n- The **MSP search campaign and Microsoft campaign** are live with daily budgets of **$20 and $25**, respectively, but the **price offer PMAX campaign underperformed**, having generated only one low-quality lead, leading to plans for phasing it out (08:02).\n    - **Christopher Quigley noted** that the sole lead was unresponsive, reinforcing the decision to discontinue that campaign.\n    - Budget adjustments for ongoing campaigns will continue based on performance data.\n\n## **RingCentral and Competitor Landing Pages with Lead Capture**\n\nThe team is building a **RingCentral-specific landing page** with a quiz-style cost calculator designed to identify qualified leads by asking about contract dates, user counts, and pricing (12:33).\n\n- They acknowledged **Google search volume for \"RingCentral replacement\" and related terms is very low**, limiting paid campaign opportunities (10:17).\n    - **Matthew Look and Colin Costigan agreed** organic channels like email outreach, blogs, and SEO will be the primary traffic drivers.\n    - Colin will research **Microsoft Advertising’s search volume and restrictions** for RingCentral terms to explore alternatives.\n    - Early exploration of **ChatGPT-enabled ads** was mentioned as a future channel once available.\n\n- The quiz form is connected to **Gravity Forms via REST API** and successfully captures submissions, but **email notifications are not triggering**, blocking timely lead follow-up (14:12).\n    - Colin is tasked with diagnosing and fixing this notification issue, despite all settings appearing correct (18:08).\n    - The team plans to integrate form submissions with **HubSpot** for contact creation and notification once stable.\n    - They aim to create a **dynamic form template** to quickly replicate for multiple providers (e.g., Comcast), saving development time by using placeholders for page-specific data.\n\n- The landing pages will be linked with **blogs and email campaigns** to funnel visitors through multiple engagement steps, accommodating prospects at different sales funnel stages (21:42).\n\n## **Website AI Readiness and Blog Content Enhancements**\n\nThe team discussed improving the website’s **AI readiness and blog presentation**, focusing on varied post templates and image generation to enhance visual appeal and engagement (22:43).\n\n- Colin recommended **MidJourney for image generation**, citing its superior quality, quick generation of four options in under a minute, and ease of use despite billing through Discord (23:49).\n    - Lindsay will evaluate MidJourney versus alternatives like Banana Nano to decide on the best fit.\n    - The goal is to provide at least **three different blog post templates** to avoid uniformity and improve user experience.\n\n- Colin is exploring technical feasibility to support **multiple blog post templates or resource-type-specific layouts** in WordPress, enabling richer content variation (25:04).\n    - This change is intended to improve content differentiation and reader engagement without major platform overhaul.\n\n## **Process Improvements and Technical Issues**\n\nThe team encountered technical hurdles with **form notification emails** despite correct configuration, motivating a deeper dive by Colin to resolve the issue urgently (14:12).\n\n- The form submissions are visible in Gravity Forms but fail to send alerts to marketing, causing a bottleneck in lead response.\n- Integration with HubSpot for automatic contact creation and notifications is planned post-fix to streamline lead management.\n- They discussed using **dynamic placeholders in the form code** to avoid duplicating forms for each provider, improving maintainability and reducing development time.\n\n## **Campaign Performance and Market Insights**\n\nCurrent campaigns show mixed results, prompting strategic shifts.\n\n- The **MSP and Microsoft ads** have modest daily budgets and mostly stable performance, but the **PMAX price offer campaign is ineffective**, prompting plans to discontinue it (08:19).\n- Bing ads for Microsoft currently have **only one click and no form submissions**, with a cost of just **5 cents**, indicating low engagement but minimal expense (30:24).\n- The team recognizes the **lower competition in Bing ads**, offering a less crowded space for outreach despite low volume.\n- They acknowledge challenges with **search term volume and ad approval on Google and Microsoft**, particularly for replacement keywords of competitors like RingCentral.\n\n## **Strategic Vision and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is aligning on a multi-pronged approach combining **targeted landing pages, organic content, and email campaigns** to capture SMB leads and compete effectively in a constrained paid search environment.\n\n- Matthew’s vision is to build out **multiple provider-specific pages with integrated cost calculators**, linked to blogs and email outreach, to guide prospects progressively through the funnel (20:23).\n- Colin and Lindsay will focus on fixing form notifications, exploring HubSpot integration, and enabling dynamic form replication to accelerate page rollouts.\n- Keyword research and platform-specific ad term viability checks for Google and Microsoft will inform ongoing ad spend and targeting adjustments.\n- Content strategy includes enhancing blog templates and visuals with AI-generated images to boost engagement and SEO performance.","outline":null,"keywords":["SMB landing page","RingCentral","Gravity Forms","digital marketing campaigns","blog templates","AI image generation"],"overview":"- **SMB Landing Page Focus:** New page emphasizes personalized support for SMBs of 5-100 seats, with trust-building testimonials.\n- **Campaign Results:** MSP ($20) and Microsoft ($25) campaigns are ongoing, while PMAX campaign will be discontinued due to poor performance.\n- **RingCentral Page Development:** A RingCentral landing page with a lead-capturing quiz is underway, pivoting to organic channels for traffic.\n- **Technical Fixes Needed:** Form notifications are failing; integration with HubSpot is planned post-resolution for lead management efficiency.\n- **Content Strategy Enhancement:** Team aims to develop multiple blog templates and visuals using AI tools for improved engagement and SEO.","action_items":"\n**Colin Costigan**\nInvestigate and resolve Gravity Forms email notification issues on WordPress (14:40)\nConduct keyword research to confirm search volume and advertising viability for RingCentral replacement terms on Microsoft platform (10:55)\nCheck feasibility of dynamic, single form usage with placeholder titles to reduce duplicated coding for provider-specific landing pages (20:55)\nExplore new WordPress post types or templates to allow multiple blog post templates for varied layouts (24:45)\n\n**Matthew Look**\nDevelop multiple landing pages similar to RingCentral cost savings calculator for other providers such as Comcast (20:25)\nIncorporate new landing pages into blogs and email campaigns to drive traffic (21:40)\n\n**Lindsay Hall**\nCheck out Banana Nano for AI image generation as a potential tool for blog images (23:44)\nCoordinate blog post template needs and communicate requirements to Colin for development (24:00)\n\n**Unassigned**\nMaintain focus on messaging emphasizing comprehensive customer support and ''one-call'' solution post-sale for SMB clients to enhance value proposition (06:38)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"2aa65edb-a290-4a81-9686-36ba05e53e05","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
