    '{"id":"01KESJXHAF9NFTKZZBKVZ5W10E","title":"New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Organic Social Media Performance and Content Strategy**\n\nThe team confirmed that consistent content posting across the main and Fahad''s pages has driven a notable rise in organic social engagement (00:09).  \n\n- **Taylor Doerbaum highlighted the positive impact of steady posting on reducing last year’s content gaps** and boosting engagement (00:09)  \n    - Jackie Wheeler approved a new image design to refresh the AI Investigator posts, aiming to attract more attention (00:53)  \n    - Taylor noted that editing previously posted content might not revive feed visibility, so creating a fresh post with the image would better extend reach (01:15)  \n    - Jackie planned to add follow-up text emphasizing client productivity gains post-launch to avoid re-announcing the product as brand new (02:15)  \n    - Taylor will schedule the new post after receiving Jackie’s text, aiming to maintain momentum from the initial launch (02:48)  \n\n- **The best-performing ad from the current “Schedule a Demo” campaign was identified as a simple, ambiguous magnifying glass image attracting the most clicks** (16:45)  \n    - Jackie suggested the ambiguity might attract some irrelevant viewers, indicating a need to refine targeting or messaging (17:20)  \n    - Taylor agreed and noted the clean design avoids overwhelming prospects while still communicating investigation services (17:38)  \n    - The team chose to proceed with that image for future creative to maintain engagement levels (18:01)  \n\n## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Campaign and Lead Targeting**\n\nThe ABM campaign generated a valuable LinkedIn response from a key contact, confirming progress in pipeline development (03:06).  \n\n- **Taylor revealed leadership’s decision to refresh the LinkedIn and email messaging sequences and gift campaign points to support this update** aiming to improve lead generation given limited prior results (05:45)  \n    - Casual, conversational LinkedIn outreach showed more success than traditional cold emails, supporting a shift in tone (05:50)  \n    - Taylor proposed focusing on smaller, higher-quality target groups, including retargeting leads from paid media who already showed interest, to improve response rates (07:26)  \n    - Jackie agreed and planned to record a short demo video to engage the retargeted audience with a quick product overview instead of a direct sales pitch (08:15)  \n    - Taylor emphasized testing smaller audience slices (around **100 contacts**) to learn and optimize before scaling up the campaign (14:41)  \n\n- **The plan includes compiling all lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for Jackie’s review to identify suitable segments for retargeting** (12:13)  \n    - Taylor will analyze engagement data from LinkedIn and campaign manager to add highly engaged leads to the targeted list (15:06)  \n    - The team aims to leverage past paid media successes by reconnecting with warm leads to boost conversion potential (13:34)  \n    - Jackie confirmed the AI Investigator product’s broad appeal across audience segments, simplifying targeting decisions (14:12)  \n\n## **Product Marketing and Demo Video Strategy**\n\nJackie is developing a **short, gated demo video** to showcase key AI Investigator features, designed as a teaser to encourage demo bookings without revealing full product capabilities (08:15).  \n\n- **Taylor cautioned that the video must leave viewers wanting more to maintain lead generation via scheduled demos** (09:17)  \n    - Jackie plans to highlight core UI elements and workflow steps, ending with a clear invitation to schedule a personalized walkthrough (10:04)  \n    - The video will be hosted on a password-protected WordPress page accessible via shared links, minimizing IP exposure while allowing easy distribution (11:02)  \n    - This gated approach balances accessibility for interested leads with protection against competitor access (11:22)  \n\n- **The video will be incorporated into the refreshed ABM campaign as a follow-up or part of outreach to segmented leads** to increase engagement and conversion rates (11:46)  \n    - Jackie targets completing the recording and initial email draft by next week to enable timely campaign launch (18:59)  \n    - Taylor offered to draft initial messaging for the email sequence to align with Jackie’s style and video content (18:39)  \n\n## **Lead Generation Content and Asset Tracking**\n\nTaylor will provide a detailed spreadsheet linking lead gen contacts to specific downloaded content assets to clarify which materials resonate most with prospects (16:06).  \n\n- **Jackie expressed interest in distinguishing between the eBook, buyer’s guide, and data sheets to understand content performance better** (15:20)  \n    - Taylor will organize and label lead data by asset type to support targeted follow-ups and messaging refinement (16:26)  \n    - This granular insight will help tailor future content offers and prioritize assets driving the highest engagement (16:34)  \n\n- **The refreshed data sheets are under development, with Fahad scheduled to review social post suggestions soon, maintaining alignment between marketing and product messaging** (18:21)  \n    - Taylor will resend updated social content sheets for Fahad’s input to refine messaging further (18:22)  \n    - This iterative collaboration aims to keep messaging fresh and relevant across channels (18:37)","outline":null,"keywords":["AI Investigator","ABM campaign","LinkedIn outreach","paid media retargeting","demo video teaser","social media engagement"],"overview":"- **Organic Social Media Engagement:** Consistent content posting has significantly increased organic engagement across main and Fahad''s pages.  \n- **Ad Campaign Insights:** The successful demo ad features a simple magnifying glass image but needs refined targeting for better engagement.  \n- **ABM Campaign Updates:** Leadership decided to revamp LinkedIn and email outreach strategies, focusing on casual tones and smaller target groups.  \n- **Demo Video Strategy:** A short, gated demo video will showcase AI Investigator features while maintaining curiosity to encourage demo bookings.  \n- **Lead Generation Tracking:** A detailed spreadsheet will link lead contacts to specific content to better understand engagement and drive future strategies.  \n- **Collaboration on Messaging:** Iterative collaboration between marketing and product teams aims to keep messaging relevant and aligned across platforms.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nPull and compile all paid media lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for review (11:59)\nSend compiled lead list and links to specific content assets downloaded by contacts to Jackie Wheeler after the meeting (03:00)\nProvide drafts of email messaging for the AI Investigator teaser video sequence for Jackie’s review and edits (18:39)\nSend refreshed data sheets to Fahad for feedback and post scheduling (18:21)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nAdd follow-up text to social media post document emphasizing positive productivity changes since launch (02:15)\nRecord a short AI Investigator demo video teaser showing UI highlights and leaving a CTA for scheduling a full demo (08:15)\nDraft the initial outreach email copy for the new test campaign including the video teaser to send to targeted contacts (18:59)\nReview paid media lead spreadsheet sent by Taylor and confirm suitability for the AI Investigator campaign or suggest alternate target groups (11:59)\n"},"duration":20.059999465942383,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"id":1,"name":"Jackie Wheeler"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Good.","index":0,"end_time":0.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How are you doing this week?","index":1,"end_time":1.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Pretty good.","index":2,"end_time":2.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Fahad will not be in the meeting.","index":3,"end_time":5.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"He''s got other things going on, so we can just jump right in.","index":4,"end_time":9.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Sounds great.","index":5,"end_time":10.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, let me pull up this agenda.","index":6,"end_time":14.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, so just wanted to start off with.","index":7,"end_time":21.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":16.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Wanted to show you a couple stats on organic social.","index":8,"end_time":24.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''re seeing a lot of upticks here, which is really great.","index":9,"end_time":26.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think the consistency that we''ve had across the main page and Fahad''s page has been really helpful for that because there was kind of a ebb and flow last year when we didn''t have content running.","index":10,"end_time":35.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":26.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the consistency has been really good.","index":11,"end_time":37.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":35.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So happy to see that.","index":12,"end_time":38.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then thank you for giving the feedback on the post that I sent you.","index":13,"end_time":42.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then I did get, just before this meeting, I got this image back from our design team that you were talking about to kind of give the AI investigators kind of a new look.","index":14,"end_time":52.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is this kind of what you''re looking for?","index":15,"end_time":53.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Totally.","index":16,"end_time":54.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":53.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":17,"end_time":54.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":54.43,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Just anything like that to give it some pop because it''s empty right now, so.","index":18,"end_time":58.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":54.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":19,"end_time":58.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":58.15,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So if.","index":20,"end_time":59.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":58.75,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Can you edit that post and add that or should do I need to do.","index":21,"end_time":62.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":59.51,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I can see if I can do it from my end.","index":22,"end_time":64.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So you want it to go with the post that''s already been posted?","index":23,"end_time":67.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, unless there''s a downside to that.","index":24,"end_time":70.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.65,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I was just thinking if you add that and then it might give it fresh life.","index":25,"end_time":75.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":71.33,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, we can add it in.","index":26,"end_time":77.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The only thing I''m thinking is if it''s already been through the feed since it''s a previous post, like the timeline of it had already passed.","index":27,"end_time":83.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So then people might not see it unless they go back to the main page.","index":28,"end_time":86.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":83.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could kind of alter the text and create a new post and then attach this image, like maybe after another one to just kind of break up the announcement.","index":29,"end_time":96.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we could do it that way because I don''t know if it''ll pop back into feeds just because an image was edited since it''s already been posted and its live time was passed.","index":30,"end_time":106.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":98.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":31,"end_time":107.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we could.","index":32,"end_time":108.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":107.74,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, a couple of those options in the sheet.","index":33,"end_time":112.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you just want to tweak them or make them more how you''d want it to go.","index":34,"end_time":116.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":112.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I had created two before you had posted, so it''s up to you.","index":35,"end_time":121.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Unless you want to just rewrite one and then we can just add this image and whatever is easiest for you.","index":36,"end_time":125.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":121.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you want to add it to the document that I sent you, then we can just go ahead and I''ll schedule it after I schedule something else.","index":37,"end_time":133.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":125.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can just break up the announcement?","index":38,"end_time":135.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m thinking we could.","index":39,"end_time":137.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":135.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"We could probably do something along the lines of clients are already seeing a massive increase in their productivity since we announced this.","index":40,"end_time":145.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":138.58,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"You got to check this out.","index":41,"end_time":147.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":146.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Something along those lines.","index":42,"end_time":148.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":147.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":43,"end_time":149.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":148.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":44,"end_time":150.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":149.72,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let me put.","index":45,"end_time":150.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.32,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Throw some text in there and then.","index":46,"end_time":152.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, just give it a.","index":47,"end_time":155.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":154,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Give it a look, see if you think there''s anything else we could say about it.","index":48,"end_time":158.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":155.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But yeah, I don''t want it to sound like it''s a brand new announcement because we already announced it, but a quick follow up, like this has been an incredible launch set the kind of thing.","index":49,"end_time":166,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.04,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":50,"end_time":167.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":166.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll do that.","index":51,"end_time":168.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":167.04,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":52,"end_time":169.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let me make a note to myself here before I forget.","index":53,"end_time":171.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":169.52,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Add text to social doc.","index":54,"end_time":177.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":172.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And I can send it over again too after the meeting.","index":55,"end_time":182.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":180.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The link.","index":56,"end_time":183.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":182.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''d be great.","index":57,"end_time":184.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":58,"end_time":185.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":184.61,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I know a lot of things can get lost in our Slack messages.","index":59,"end_time":188.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t know if you know, but do you know how that call went that we were able to get through the EBM campaign that had.","index":60,"end_time":197.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":190.85,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, he said that he.","index":61,"end_time":200.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.65,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"She was the right person to talk to that she''s like, involved in.","index":62,"end_time":205.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":200.21,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think it was a she.","index":63,"end_time":206.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":205.4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Anyway, it doesn''t matter that they were involved in multiple different groups and in the company.","index":64,"end_time":212.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":206.28,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And so now it''s about getting in front of other people.","index":65,"end_time":214.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":212.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So that''s in progress.","index":66,"end_time":216.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":215.16,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it sounds like it was, you know, just awesome.","index":67,"end_time":219.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":216.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I was so excited when I saw that when I logged in the next morning, it had like come in really late the night before and I was like, oh, my gosh, we need to get this.","index":68,"end_time":228.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Get this scheduled.","index":69,"end_time":229.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":228.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So usually it''s hard to get people to show up.","index":70,"end_time":232.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And.","index":71,"end_time":232.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":232.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And that one came through a LinkedIn.","index":72,"end_time":234.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":232.53,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"LinkedIn sequence.","index":73,"end_time":236.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was the ABM sequence.","index":74,"end_time":237.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":236.09,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":75,"end_time":237.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it was the.","index":76,"end_time":238.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it was the first message that we had sent.","index":77,"end_time":241.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":238.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it wasn''t even the one where he was like, I think, offering a schedule call.","index":78,"end_time":246.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":242.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was the one that said would love to connect and like share ideas.","index":79,"end_time":251.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":246.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s like that first message before the actual cta.","index":80,"end_time":254.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that was cool to kind of see how she took it as.","index":81,"end_time":256.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, let''s chat now.","index":82,"end_time":257.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":256.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So.","index":83,"end_time":258.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that was great.","index":84,"end_time":259.559,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":258.359,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And was it one of the people that was on the list of lawyers that Jeffrey''s been sending over or was it a rando?","index":85,"end_time":267.159,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260.039,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I can look and see what exact sheet she came from, but all those lists are compiled now into the campaign.","index":86,"end_time":272.439,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.159,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So let me go see if I can pull.","index":87,"end_time":274.719,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":272.759,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I can figure out which one.","index":88,"end_time":276.119,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":274.719,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly where.","index":89,"end_time":278.599,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":277.399,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What list she came from that would.","index":90,"end_time":280.039,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":278.679,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Be just be curious to know because then maybe that helps us figure out, okay, this is our target.","index":91,"end_time":284.759,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.039,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":92,"end_time":285.399,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":284.759,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":93,"end_time":286.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":285.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s a data point of one, so that''s not super helpful.","index":94,"end_time":289.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":286.66,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But hey, one is great though.","index":95,"end_time":290.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":289.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m glad we got a call.","index":96,"end_time":291.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Agreed.","index":97,"end_time":293.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Agreed.","index":98,"end_time":293.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":293.14,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, look into that and see.","index":99,"end_time":296.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":294.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s funny because I was just thinking like, oh, we really need to change this up a little.","index":100,"end_time":301.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":297.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then that happened.","index":101,"end_time":302.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But still, I do think it''s good to refresh.","index":102,"end_time":304.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":302.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I''ve been thinking about it, I''ve been talking with my leadership on our end of things and um, obviously it''s really great that we got that response back.","index":103,"end_time":314.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":305.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":104,"end_time":314.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":314.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as the LinkedIn side of things, and I think that it something a testament to that is the casual conversation of saying like, let''s connect and share ideas instead of it being like a super salesy thing which can come across sometimes more in email.","index":105,"end_time":326.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":314.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Um, and I have seen more success across LinkedIn usually for my clients.","index":106,"end_time":330.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":327.059,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But as far as like a sequence, I was thinking we definitely need to refresh something and because this is such an important thing, obviously we want to get you guys leads and the ABM campaign is of a lot of importance.","index":107,"end_time":342.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":331.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I spoke with leadership and they want to gift you the points if we want to refresh the sequence just because we want this to be successful for you and since it hasn''t gained a ton of results yet, we want to try something different.","index":108,"end_time":355.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":342.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And the whole point of ABM is to find what works, find what doesn''t.","index":109,"end_time":359.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This particular one from the messaging sequence was really great because then we can kind of see that that was beneficial as far as like the casual conversation on the LinkedIn side of things.","index":110,"end_time":368.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But as far as email, since we haven''t yielded any results from there, I think it would be good to maybe change that up and again we would just do that on our end and gift those points.","index":111,"end_time":379.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":368.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I was thinking, I was.","index":112,"end_time":381.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.919,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have a new person that I''ve been working with on our team that is really good at abm and he just talks about how like cold email is so tough, like just getting anybody through cold email.","index":113,"end_time":391.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Which is why I said LinkedIn is usually more successful, which is really great.","index":114,"end_time":394.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":391.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But.","index":115,"end_time":395.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":395.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I think there could be something to the new AI investigator that you guys have just launched and I think that maybe putting that into a new sequence would be beneficial to see.","index":116,"end_time":406.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":395.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Kind of like you''re saying where we word it so it''s kind of, it''s new but it''s also a super helpful tool that you should check out and, and make that kind of context around it.","index":117,"end_time":418.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":406.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What I was thinking is instead of kind of adding into these thousands of contacts we have been targeting for so long, maybe we try a smaller audience of either, either if it''s something that you guys have like a list on your end and you''re like this is a group that''s smaller that we really want to target or what we can do is I was thinking we re engaged audience, people from like our paid media.","index":118,"end_time":442.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":418.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the people that have filled out those lead gen forms, we have all of their emails.","index":119,"end_time":446.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":442.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that could be a really small group of targeting that we test out because they have interest, they know your brand, they, they''ve downloaded our, the content we''ve offered.","index":120,"end_time":454.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":446.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that might be something that we can retarget them into a campaign.","index":121,"end_time":457.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":454.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And whether that is about the AI investigator, I can compile all of those contacts into one spreadsheet and if you guys want to look it over and say this might not be the audience because I know that there''s so many different categories of your audience for the AI investigator and then we can make it kind of more catered to those people.","index":122,"end_time":476.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I think pulling contacts out and kind of eliminating how big the list is will be helpful and maybe getting a response if it''s kind of more catered to a particular set of people instead of like this giant, giant group we have running of 3,000, 4,000.","index":123,"end_time":492.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":476.75,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So what do you think about that?","index":124,"end_time":493.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":492.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you think that would be something that would be a good idea?","index":125,"end_time":495.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":493.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it''s, yeah, I think it''s a good idea.","index":126,"end_time":497.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":495.86,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I, you know, this video that I''m about to record, I finally got my mic working again so I''m going to record this, this quick demo.","index":127,"end_time":503.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.58,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think that also you know, highlights the AI investigator.","index":128,"end_time":506.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":503.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think that that could be an approach with this group and say no time for a demo here.","index":129,"end_time":512.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":507.06,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Take a look at this quick two minute video that highlights the key features that we think will really help you.","index":130,"end_time":518.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.66,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It can be super short like that.","index":131,"end_time":520.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":518.66,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Again, casual conversation I think is going to get more than all the salesy kind of language and all the AI generated stuff.","index":132,"end_time":527.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":520.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So you know, again I just want to double down on authenticity and you know, more person to person kind of attitude.","index":133,"end_time":535.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.7,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"This demo, quick video, I think will, will be something really easy to click that people can get a quick view of the product and it''s like I don''t have time to book a demo, but I can take a quick look at this so that''s kind of what I''m thinking would be a really useful thing.","index":134,"end_time":551.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":535.87,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it''s not just words.","index":135,"end_time":554.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":552.99,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":136,"end_time":555.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What do you think about that?","index":137,"end_time":556.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":555.47,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"The only thing I worry about with that is we''re giving away, like, what we''re asking for in return.","index":138,"end_time":562.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":557.15,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we wouldn''t see maybe as many leads come through that.","index":139,"end_time":566.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because you''re giving them what they would book a call to see if that makes sense.","index":140,"end_time":571.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":566.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, it''s.","index":141,"end_time":571.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":571.2,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But it''s a teaser because it''s only showing a few things.","index":142,"end_time":574.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":571.76,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So if you''re able to, like, when you record it, kind of leave them hanging at the end.","index":143,"end_time":579.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":574.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":144,"end_time":579.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.04,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That would be good.","index":145,"end_time":580.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":579.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s the whole point.","index":146,"end_time":581.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.6,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"That''s the only thing I worry about is, like, if we explain it all on a thing, they''re like, why would I call you?","index":147,"end_time":585.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":581.56,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because I already watched it.","index":148,"end_time":586.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":585.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, if you''re.","index":149,"end_time":587.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":586.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If you''re gonna kind of like, give it a little tease, and then at the end we kind of like, come in and be like, you know, leave them hanging, then I think that would be beneficial.","index":150,"end_time":594.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":587.36,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we could even have like, a CTA afterwards.","index":151,"end_time":597.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":594.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, do you want to learn more about this?","index":152,"end_time":599.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or I don''t know if you''re going to walk through, like, a particular case or something like that, or like, it''s.","index":153,"end_time":604.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Going to be just the quick highlights.","index":154,"end_time":606.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":604.87,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it''s going to say, so let''s say you''re.","index":155,"end_time":608.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.19,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"You.","index":156,"end_time":608.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.19,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"You''ve got a case where you''re supposed to investigate Baywater.","index":157,"end_time":610.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.43,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Well, the first place people, like, here''s the dashboard.","index":158,"end_time":613.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":610.95,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But the place people like to start is the AI investigator.","index":159,"end_time":615.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":613.15,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Here''s a couple questions you might ask.","index":160,"end_time":617.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":615.67,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It gives you guidance on where to go.","index":161,"end_time":618.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":617.35,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And now you''re going to go and check out your parties and then like, show them one other screen and go.","index":162,"end_time":623.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.97,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"This is just scratching the surface, but these.","index":163,"end_time":625.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":623.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But, you know, let''s.","index":164,"end_time":626.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":625.52,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let''s schedule a demo so we can look through your date, talk about how this is going to apply to your cases, what you''re working on, and we''ll give you a full walkthrough of what the.","index":165,"end_time":635.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":626.64,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"What the product can do for you.","index":166,"end_time":636.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":635.12,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So it''s a.","index":167,"end_time":637.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.8,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s nothing but a teaser, but it gives them something to see, something to.","index":168,"end_time":641.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":637.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Hold on to, to kind of introduce it better than, like a just copy would.","index":169,"end_time":645.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":641.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, just then words or a static picture would.","index":170,"end_time":648.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":645.28,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So, yeah, that''s the idea.","index":171,"end_time":649.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":648.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Would you want this embedded on a page or would you want to just send the video?","index":172,"end_time":653.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, how was your idea of setting this up?","index":173,"end_time":655.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":653.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Was it going to be like, Living on the like a guarded like site page that was only accessible through a link that we''d send through an email.","index":174,"end_time":662.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s kind of what I''m thinking.","index":175,"end_time":663.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like let''s keep it gated for the time being without them having to put in any information obviously, because we already have their contact information.","index":176,"end_time":671.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":663.96,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But yes, a link that is only available if you have the link and of course they can share the link and it''s not going to give away any IP or anything like that.","index":177,"end_time":681.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":672.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So.","index":178,"end_time":683.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":682.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it''s not going to, you know, our competitors are not going to jump on this and see all the things that we do but any more than our screenshots already do that are on the website.","index":179,"end_time":692.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":683.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So yeah, I think that''s, I think that''s the way to do it is to host it on the website somewhere.","index":180,"end_time":700.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":693.14,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I just, I''ll just upload it into WordPress.","index":181,"end_time":703.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.79,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Would you think for that video particular.","index":182,"end_time":708.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":706.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is there a particular audience of people that you have in mind that this would go to?","index":183,"end_time":712.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":708.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Would this be a particular group that maybe Fahad and are going to pull or.","index":184,"end_time":717.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think your ABM campaign is the.","index":185,"end_time":719.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718.11,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Perfect place for added into the current one.","index":186,"end_time":722.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":719.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What?","index":187,"end_time":723.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":722.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Well, this new you''re talking about.","index":188,"end_time":727.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.31,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":189,"end_time":727.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":727.03,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Like it could be a follow up to people we''ve already.","index":190,"end_time":730.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":727.39,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"To all the people we''ve already reached out to.","index":191,"end_time":733.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.15,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":192,"end_time":733.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or it could be a new, like a new part of the new lists or.","index":193,"end_time":739.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":733.93,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I''m not sure.","index":194,"end_time":740.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":739.81,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"What do you think?","index":195,"end_time":740.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":740.33,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it just depends.","index":196,"end_time":743.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":741.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think what I''m going to do after this call is I''m going to go pull all of the leads we''ve gotten from lead Gen.","index":197,"end_time":747.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.05,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m going to put them into one spreadsheet and then I''m going to send that over to you guys.","index":198,"end_time":751.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And if you want to review that, if they''re all over the board and like this wouldn''t apply to a lot of them, maybe they don''t have a title that you''re looking for, then I wouldn''t recommend doing that.","index":199,"end_time":758.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":751.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"However, we may be able to retarget them through through another means.","index":200,"end_time":762.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":759.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like if we created a small sequence to just have them jump on a call and then maybe Fahad can talk with them and see what their needs are.","index":201,"end_time":769.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":762.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But then if that doesn''t work out for the AI investigator side of things, whatever group you guys think would be beneficial for that audience.","index":202,"end_time":777.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like if maybe there''s just one of the lists we want to.","index":203,"end_time":779.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could even test too.","index":204,"end_time":781.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So all those lists that Jeffrey sends each week, if we just want to take one of Those lists and use them as kind of our test and send your video to that group and then we can learn from that audience.","index":205,"end_time":790.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":781.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if that''s super successful, then we can apply it to the other campaign spreadsheets that we have running.","index":206,"end_time":796.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":790.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I think testing it in a smaller portion would be beneficial.","index":207,"end_time":798.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"First we can learn the audience, which is kind of how we do abm, is we want to learn from it.","index":208,"end_time":803.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then that way we''re not sending it out to 4,000 contacts, which slows down a campaign totally.","index":209,"end_time":808.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":803.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So this way we can get through the campaign faster and learn the audience better.","index":210,"end_time":811.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, that makes perfect sense.","index":211,"end_time":813.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":812.22,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m going to pull those.","index":212,"end_time":815.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it''s super beneficial to retarget the people that are engaging with paid media.","index":213,"end_time":819.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And you guys have had, I have it on here, a lot of success through the Legion campaigns.","index":214,"end_time":824.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":819.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just pulled some data this morning.","index":215,"end_time":826,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":824.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And, you know, if these people are interested in your content that we''re offering and they''re familiar with your brand, they''re going to see said draw and they''re going to know it.","index":216,"end_time":834.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":826,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it would just be good to kind of familiarize them again with, with what you offer.","index":217,"end_time":839.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":834.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So.","index":218,"end_time":840.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":839.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":219,"end_time":841.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":840.12,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I imagine the AI Investigator, though, if somebody is downloading these things, it would be beneficial to somebody interested in all of these categories.","index":220,"end_time":849.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":841.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is that correct?","index":221,"end_time":850.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":849.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or would you say it''s more of a niche?","index":222,"end_time":851.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, I mean, the, the AI Investigator is going to apply to everybody.","index":223,"end_time":856.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.42,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Maybe it would, would work for these, for these particular set of people, for sure.","index":224,"end_time":860.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":856.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, but the, the video is like, it''s a quick look at the, at the user interface.","index":225,"end_time":867.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":860.9,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"And so that''s going to apply to everybody too.","index":226,"end_time":870.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":867.22,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Anybody.","index":227,"end_time":871.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":870.9,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So, yeah, I don''t, I don''t think we need to think about any kind of a niche with this.","index":228,"end_time":877.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":872.34,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s anybody who would be interested in Cedra.","index":229,"end_time":879.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":877.74,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"This is, this is for them.","index":230,"end_time":880.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":879.66,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Great, that''s good to know.","index":231,"end_time":882.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":881.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Then that makes it easier for us to pull that audience then.","index":232,"end_time":884.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if we wanted to, like, we could either go with just this small group or we could add, maybe make it a hundred contacts.","index":233,"end_time":892.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":885.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can pull from another spreadsheet we have, or we could enrich the list.","index":234,"end_time":896.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":892.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Whatever you guys think is best.","index":235,"end_time":898.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":896.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we could maybe make it like a hundred people and run that campaign and see how that performs.","index":236,"end_time":904.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":898.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":237,"end_time":905.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":904.98,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yes.","index":238,"end_time":906.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":906.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then we can also just take a look at our analytics and, and the campaign manager and LinkedIn and see if there''s any additional people that we''ve noticed, engage a lot with the content and then we can add them to that list as well.","index":239,"end_time":917.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":906.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think that''d be a really good idea.","index":240,"end_time":919.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":918.24,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So what''s the difference between the E book free guide and buyer''s guide?","index":241,"end_time":923.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":920.08,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yes.","index":242,"end_time":924.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":923.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So these are the different things that we''re offering.","index":243,"end_time":927.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":924.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we have the different lead gen campaigns that are running.","index":244,"end_time":931.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":927.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the financial.","index":245,"end_time":932,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the ebook was the.","index":246,"end_time":933.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"One of the assets that we had.","index":247,"end_time":935.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":933.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then those data sheets.","index":248,"end_time":937.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":935.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So those are also on the lead.","index":249,"end_time":938.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":937.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Right.","index":250,"end_time":939.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":938.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But isn''t the E book and the buyer''s guide the same thing or is that something else?","index":251,"end_time":942.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.16,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think it was the one pager because we had the one pager.","index":252,"end_time":945.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":942.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Maybe let me pull up the exact camp.","index":253,"end_time":949.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":946.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I should know this, but I''m.","index":254,"end_time":950.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":949.48,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"There''s so many different.","index":255,"end_time":952.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":951.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Gone.","index":256,"end_time":953,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":952.44,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":257,"end_time":953.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":953.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s gone.","index":258,"end_time":954.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":953.96,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It also must be.","index":259,"end_time":955.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":954.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It also could be listed in a separate campaign, which makes it a different title.","index":260,"end_time":959.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":955.76,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":261,"end_time":960.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":959.8,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":262,"end_time":961.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":960.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because I''m just curious what content is resonating.","index":263,"end_time":963.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":961.28,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It''s not letting me pull it up here because I''m not logged in.","index":264,"end_time":969.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s not letting me pull it up.","index":265,"end_time":976.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":975.65,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But after this call I can send.","index":266,"end_time":978.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":976.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I can add the links to the spreadsheet of the particular assets if that''s helpful.","index":267,"end_time":982.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":978.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, it would be.","index":268,"end_time":983.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":982.77,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I just.","index":269,"end_time":984.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":983.53,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I''d like to know, like I''ll split.","index":270,"end_time":986.329,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.21,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It up to like in sections like you''re saying.","index":271,"end_time":988.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":986.329,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll link the exact asset that they downloaded and put it all into one spot.","index":272,"end_time":993.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":273,"end_time":993.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":993.05,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":274,"end_time":994.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":993.61,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":275,"end_time":995.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":994.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But anyway, yeah, I think that would be good to retarget those particular people.","index":276,"end_time":1001.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":997.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Where it says best performing ad and campaign link.","index":277,"end_time":1004.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1001.45,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Oh yes.","index":278,"end_time":1005.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1005.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This was for the schedule a demo campaign that we''re running right now.","index":279,"end_time":1009.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1006.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This one is very highly the favorited one out of what we have running.","index":280,"end_time":1015.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1009.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So sometimes we like to learn from this.","index":281,"end_time":1018.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1015.29,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So when I have our creative team design ads in the future, if there''s something that stands out more than all the other ones, we try to kind of mimic that but change it up a little bit.","index":282,"end_time":1027.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So of all the different like image ads we had running, this is the one that was most appealing to people.","index":283,"end_time":1032.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I guess it was clicked on the most and yeah.","index":284,"end_time":1035.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The most clicks and views that we''ve had on this one.","index":285,"end_time":1038.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1035.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I just share that with you.","index":286,"end_time":1040.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1038.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s interesting.","index":287,"end_time":1040.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.07,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I wonder if partially because it''s kind of ambiguous, it doesn''t talk about financial investigations, it just says it''s not anymore.","index":288,"end_time":1048.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1040.67,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It might be that a lot of it might be popular, but maybe with the wrong people.","index":289,"end_time":1053.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1048.99,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Because it might be.","index":290,"end_time":1054.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1053.71,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":291,"end_time":1055.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1055.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Anyway, something to.","index":292,"end_time":1057.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1055.91,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Something to consider.","index":293,"end_time":1058.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1057.63,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":294,"end_time":1059.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The good thing about this is we Kind of did a play on this, actually.","index":295,"end_time":1061.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1059.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we.","index":296,"end_time":1063.469,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1062.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is a successful, like the magnifying glass effect.","index":297,"end_time":1066.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.469,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it''s like a clean way to talk about investigations without making it look, you know, overbearing.","index":298,"end_time":1070.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1066.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yep, I like it.","index":299,"end_time":1071.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1070.83,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So did you have a preference as to where the logo is located for either of these or which one do you prefer as far as imagery?","index":300,"end_time":1079.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1072.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No, I think.","index":301,"end_time":1084.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.89,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"I think they both look cool.","index":302,"end_time":1085.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1084.33,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"So whatever you guys think is the.","index":303,"end_time":1086.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1085.45,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Best one, I would say this one.","index":304,"end_time":1088.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1086.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just because we''ve highlighted investigations like twice here and I think it only needs to be.","index":305,"end_time":1092.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1088.13,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, yeah, yeah, yeah, I agree with you.","index":306,"end_time":1094.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1092.29,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let''s do that one.","index":307,"end_time":1094.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1094.09,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":308,"end_time":1096.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1095.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, we will.","index":309,"end_time":1097.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1096.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ll do that then.","index":310,"end_time":1098.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1097.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the only other updates I had is we''re working on those data sheet refreshes.","index":311,"end_time":1101.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":312,"end_time":1102.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1101.89,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Sent us.","index":313,"end_time":1103.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1102.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m going to send that sheet over to Fahad again so we can get his input on some posts that we can do.","index":314,"end_time":1108.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1104.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then the organic scheduling on our end of the other post that we had already talked about and adding in that new image will be good.","index":315,"end_time":1115.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1108.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Very cool.","index":316,"end_time":1115.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1115.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":317,"end_time":1117.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1117.12,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Thanks for all your support.","index":318,"end_time":1118.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1117.96,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Of course.","index":319,"end_time":1120,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1119.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as the messaging around this video and kind of how that sequence could look, I can write a couple drafts and send them over to you, and then you can make any changes according to how you''re going to kind of speak through the video.","index":320,"end_time":1133,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1120,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And did you have a timeline of when you think that will be done and when we could launch this.","index":321,"end_time":1137.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1133.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This test campaign?","index":322,"end_time":1138.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1137.8,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m hoping next week.","index":323,"end_time":1140.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1139.24,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m planning to record it today, so we''ll see how it goes.","index":324,"end_time":1143.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1141.32,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"It could be done today, but let''s.","index":325,"end_time":1146.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1143.88,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Let''s see how that goes and then.","index":326,"end_time":1148.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1146.52,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"No, I''m happy to write the draft for the email, the initial email that''ll go out about it.","index":327,"end_time":1154.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1149.4,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Because I''ve got kind of an idea of what I want to say about this.","index":328,"end_time":1156.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1154.36,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"But anyway, yeah, let me take a first cut at it, but if you have any ideas, feel free to send them over.","index":329,"end_time":1161.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1156.84,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":330,"end_time":1161.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.66,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":331,"end_time":1162.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.94,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That sounds good.","index":332,"end_time":1163.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1162.62,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m excited to work on this.","index":333,"end_time":1164.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1163.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''ll be fun to test new audience.","index":334,"end_time":1167.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1164.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Great.","index":335,"end_time":1168.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1167.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Well, I hope you have a good rest of your day, Jackie.","index":336,"end_time":1169.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1168.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You too.","index":337,"end_time":1170.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1169.98,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Thanks so much.","index":338,"end_time":1171.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1170.38,"speaker_name":"Jackie Wheeler"},{"text":"Bye.","index":339,"end_time":1171.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Bye.","index":340,"end_time":1172.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1171.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"dateString":"2026-01-14T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/88927304763?pwd=asbbQolEtVpMuYX5uccJpOibhnlog1.1","participants":["taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com,baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com,j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com,i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com,f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com","baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","j.wheeler@sedrasolutions.com","i.hamshari@sedrasolutions.com","f.almutawa@sedrasolutions.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KESJXHAF9NFTKZZBKVZ5W10E","organizer_email":"taylor.doerbaum@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.92,"bullets":["Reported significant upticks in organic social performance due to improved consistency across channels.","Proposed refreshed ABM campaign messaging with LinkedIn focus based on early engagement success.","Planned to retarget high-intent paid media leads through a gated teaser video demo by next week.","Agreed to test new AI Investigator messaging on 100-contact segment to optimize outreach strategy.","Confirmed creative direction for ad imagery based on best-performing visuals in current campaign."],"highlights":[{"quote":"The consistency that we''ve had... has been really helpful for that.","speaker":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"quote":"We want this to be successful for you and since it hasn''t gained a ton of results yet, we want to try something different.","speaker":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"quote":"This demo, quick video... will be something really easy to click.","speaker":"Jackie Wheeler"}],"topics":["campaign","delivery","engagement","ABM","content"],"model":"gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-16T19:44:08Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Organic Social Media Performance and Content Strategy**\n\nThe team confirmed that consistent content posting across the main and Fahad''s pages has driven a notable rise in organic social engagement (00:09).  \n\n- **Taylor Doerbaum highlighted the positive impact of steady posting on reducing last year’s content gaps** and boosting engagement (00:09)  \n    - Jackie Wheeler approved a new image design to refresh the AI Investigator posts, aiming to attract more attention (00:53)  \n    - Taylor noted that editing previously posted content might not revive feed visibility, so creating a fresh post with the image would better extend reach (01:15)  \n    - Jackie planned to add follow-up text emphasizing client productivity gains post-launch to avoid re-announcing the product as brand new (02:15)  \n    - Taylor will schedule the new post after receiving Jackie’s text, aiming to maintain momentum from the initial launch (02:48)  \n\n- **The best-performing ad from the current “Schedule a Demo” campaign was identified as a simple, ambiguous magnifying glass image attracting the most clicks** (16:45)  \n    - Jackie suggested the ambiguity might attract some irrelevant viewers, indicating a need to refine targeting or messaging (17:20)  \n    - Taylor agreed and noted the clean design avoids overwhelming prospects while still communicating investigation services (17:38)  \n    - The team chose to proceed with that image for future creative to maintain engagement levels (18:01)  \n\n## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Campaign and Lead Targeting**\n\nThe ABM campaign generated a valuable LinkedIn response from a key contact, confirming progress in pipeline development (03:06).  \n\n- **Taylor revealed leadership’s decision to refresh the LinkedIn and email messaging sequences and gift campaign points to support this update** aiming to improve lead generation given limited prior results (05:45)  \n    - Casual, conversational LinkedIn outreach showed more success than traditional cold emails, supporting a shift in tone (05:50)  \n    - Taylor proposed focusing on smaller, higher-quality target groups, including retargeting leads from paid media who already showed interest, to improve response rates (07:26)  \n    - Jackie agreed and planned to record a short demo video to engage the retargeted audience with a quick product overview instead of a direct sales pitch (08:15)  \n    - Taylor emphasized testing smaller audience slices (around **100 contacts**) to learn and optimize before scaling up the campaign (14:41)  \n\n- **The plan includes compiling all lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for Jackie’s review to identify suitable segments for retargeting** (12:13)  \n    - Taylor will analyze engagement data from LinkedIn and campaign manager to add highly engaged leads to the targeted list (15:06)  \n    - The team aims to leverage past paid media successes by reconnecting with warm leads to boost conversion potential (13:34)  \n    - Jackie confirmed the AI Investigator product’s broad appeal across audience segments, simplifying targeting decisions (14:12)  \n\n## **Product Marketing and Demo Video Strategy**\n\nJackie is developing a **short, gated demo video** to showcase key AI Investigator features, designed as a teaser to encourage demo bookings without revealing full product capabilities (08:15).  \n\n- **Taylor cautioned that the video must leave viewers wanting more to maintain lead generation via scheduled demos** (09:17)  \n    - Jackie plans to highlight core UI elements and workflow steps, ending with a clear invitation to schedule a personalized walkthrough (10:04)  \n    - The video will be hosted on a password-protected WordPress page accessible via shared links, minimizing IP exposure while allowing easy distribution (11:02)  \n    - This gated approach balances accessibility for interested leads with protection against competitor access (11:22)  \n\n- **The video will be incorporated into the refreshed ABM campaign as a follow-up or part of outreach to segmented leads** to increase engagement and conversion rates (11:46)  \n    - Jackie targets completing the recording and initial email draft by next week to enable timely campaign launch (18:59)  \n    - Taylor offered to draft initial messaging for the email sequence to align with Jackie’s style and video content (18:39)  \n\n## **Lead Generation Content and Asset Tracking**\n\nTaylor will provide a detailed spreadsheet linking lead gen contacts to specific downloaded content assets to clarify which materials resonate most with prospects (16:06).  \n\n- **Jackie expressed interest in distinguishing between the eBook, buyer’s guide, and data sheets to understand content performance better** (15:20)  \n    - Taylor will organize and label lead data by asset type to support targeted follow-ups and messaging refinement (16:26)  \n    - This granular insight will help tailor future content offers and prioritize assets driving the highest engagement (16:34)  \n\n- **The refreshed data sheets are under development, with Fahad scheduled to review social post suggestions soon, maintaining alignment between marketing and product messaging** (18:21)  \n    - Taylor will resend updated social content sheets for Fahad’s input to refine messaging further (18:22)  \n    - This iterative collaboration aims to keep messaging fresh and relevant across channels (18:37)","outline":null,"keywords":["AI Investigator","ABM campaign","LinkedIn outreach","paid media retargeting","demo video teaser","social media engagement"],"overview":"- **Organic Social Media Engagement:** Consistent content posting has significantly increased organic engagement across main and Fahad''s pages.  \n- **Ad Campaign Insights:** The successful demo ad features a simple magnifying glass image but needs refined targeting for better engagement.  \n- **ABM Campaign Updates:** Leadership decided to revamp LinkedIn and email outreach strategies, focusing on casual tones and smaller target groups.  \n- **Demo Video Strategy:** A short, gated demo video will showcase AI Investigator features while maintaining curiosity to encourage demo bookings.  \n- **Lead Generation Tracking:** A detailed spreadsheet will link lead contacts to specific content to better understand engagement and drive future strategies.  \n- **Collaboration on Messaging:** Iterative collaboration between marketing and product teams aims to keep messaging relevant and aligned across platforms.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nPull and compile all paid media lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for review (11:59)\nSend compiled lead list and links to specific content assets downloaded by contacts to Jackie Wheeler after the meeting (03:00)\nProvide drafts of email messaging for the AI Investigator teaser video sequence for Jackie’s review and edits (18:39)\nSend refreshed data sheets to Fahad for feedback and post scheduling (18:21)\n\n**Jackie Wheeler**\nAdd follow-up text to social media post document emphasizing positive productivity changes since launch (02:15)\nRecord a short AI Investigator demo video teaser showing UI highlights and leaving a CTA for scheduling a full demo (08:15)\nDraft the initial outreach email copy for the new test campaign including the video teaser to send to targeted contacts (18:59)\nReview paid media lead spreadsheet sent by Taylor and confirm suitability for the AI Investigator campaign or suggest alternate target groups (11:59)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"ba1bd80f-de7c-4631-8ad9-d58926fb05a8","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
    '2026-01-16 22:05:47.680098+00',
