INSERT INTO compass_notes (contract_id, meeting_id, note_type, title, content_raw, note_date, status, action_items, is_auto_generated)
SELECT
  new_meeting.contract_id,
  new_meeting.meeting_id,
  'meeting',
  'Meeting Notes: New North x Sedra Solutions: Weekly Meeting',
  '## **Organic Social Media Performance and Content Strategy**

The team confirmed that consistent content posting across the main and Fahad''s pages has driven a notable rise in organic social engagement (00:09).  

- **Taylor Doerbaum highlighted the positive impact of steady posting on reducing last year’s content gaps** and boosting engagement (00:09)  
    - Jackie Wheeler approved a new image design to refresh the AI Investigator posts, aiming to attract more attention (00:53)  
    - Taylor noted that editing previously posted content might not revive feed visibility, so creating a fresh post with the image would better extend reach (01:15)  
    - Jackie planned to add follow-up text emphasizing client productivity gains post-launch to avoid re-announcing the product as brand new (02:15)  
    - Taylor will schedule the new post after receiving Jackie’s text, aiming to maintain momentum from the initial launch (02:48)  

- **The best-performing ad from the current “Schedule a Demo” campaign was identified as a simple, ambiguous magnifying glass image attracting the most clicks** (16:45)  
    - Jackie suggested the ambiguity might attract some irrelevant viewers, indicating a need to refine targeting or messaging (17:20)  
    - Taylor agreed and noted the clean design avoids overwhelming prospects while still communicating investigation services (17:38)  
    - The team chose to proceed with that image for future creative to maintain engagement levels (18:01)  

## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Campaign and Lead Targeting**

The ABM campaign generated a valuable LinkedIn response from a key contact, confirming progress in pipeline development (03:06).  

- **Taylor revealed leadership’s decision to refresh the LinkedIn and email messaging sequences and gift campaign points to support this update** aiming to improve lead generation given limited prior results (05:45)  
    - Casual, conversational LinkedIn outreach showed more success than traditional cold emails, supporting a shift in tone (05:50)  
    - Taylor proposed focusing on smaller, higher-quality target groups, including retargeting leads from paid media who already showed interest, to improve response rates (07:26)  
    - Jackie agreed and planned to record a short demo video to engage the retargeted audience with a quick product overview instead of a direct sales pitch (08:15)  
    - Taylor emphasized testing smaller audience slices (around **100 contacts**) to learn and optimize before scaling up the campaign (14:41)  

- **The plan includes compiling all lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for Jackie’s review to identify suitable segments for retargeting** (12:13)  
    - Taylor will analyze engagement data from LinkedIn and campaign manager to add highly engaged leads to the targeted list (15:06)  
    - The team aims to leverage past paid media successes by reconnecting with warm leads to boost conversion potential (13:34)  
    - Jackie confirmed the AI Investigator product’s broad appeal across audience segments, simplifying targeting decisions (14:12)  

## **Product Marketing and Demo Video Strategy**

Jackie is developing a **short, gated demo video** to showcase key AI Investigator features, designed as a teaser to encourage demo bookings without revealing full product capabilities (08:15).  

- **Taylor cautioned that the video must leave viewers wanting more to maintain lead generation via scheduled demos** (09:17)  
    - Jackie plans to highlight core UI elements and workflow steps, ending with a clear invitation to schedule a personalized walkthrough (10:04)  
    - The video will be hosted on a password-protected WordPress page accessible via shared links, minimizing IP exposure while allowing easy distribution (11:02)  
    - This gated approach balances accessibility for interested leads with protection against competitor access (11:22)  

- **The video will be incorporated into the refreshed ABM campaign as a follow-up or part of outreach to segmented leads** to increase engagement and conversion rates (11:46)  
    - Jackie targets completing the recording and initial email draft by next week to enable timely campaign launch (18:59)  
    - Taylor offered to draft initial messaging for the email sequence to align with Jackie’s style and video content (18:39)  

## **Lead Generation Content and Asset Tracking**

Taylor will provide a detailed spreadsheet linking lead gen contacts to specific downloaded content assets to clarify which materials resonate most with prospects (16:06).  

- **Jackie expressed interest in distinguishing between the eBook, buyer’s guide, and data sheets to understand content performance better** (15:20)  
    - Taylor will organize and label lead data by asset type to support targeted follow-ups and messaging refinement (16:26)  
    - This granular insight will help tailor future content offers and prioritize assets driving the highest engagement (16:34)  

- **The refreshed data sheets are under development, with Fahad scheduled to review social post suggestions soon, maintaining alignment between marketing and product messaging** (18:21)  
    - Taylor will resend updated social content sheets for Fahad’s input to refine messaging further (18:22)  
    - This iterative collaboration aims to keep messaging fresh and relevant across channels (18:37)',
  '2026-01-14 16:30:00+00',
  'published',
  '[{"text":"Pull and compile all paid media lead gen contacts into one spreadsheet for review (11:59)","completed":false},{"text":"Send compiled lead list and links to specific content assets downloaded by contacts to Jackie Wheeler after the meeting (03:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide drafts of email messaging for the AI Investigator teaser video sequence for Jackie’s review and edits (18:39)","completed":false},{"text":"Send refreshed data sheets to Fahad for feedback and post scheduling (18:21)","completed":false},{"text":"Add follow-up text to social media post document emphasizing positive productivity changes since launch (02:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Record a short AI Investigator demo video teaser showing UI highlights and leaving a CTA for scheduling a full demo (08:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Draft the initial outreach email copy for the new test campaign including the video teaser to send to targeted contacts (18:59)","completed":false},{"text":"Review paid media lead spreadsheet sent by Taylor and confirm suitability for the AI Investigator campaign or suggest alternate target groups (11:59)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
  true
FROM new_meeting;

-- Meeting: Hydrian // New North: Weekly Meeting (new) (2026-01-14 20:00:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'ec1251b4-8dd8-4f12-ba68-1e923a54c460',
    '2026-01-14 20:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KESXWXMZZDAX55BWVJNQFM01',
    'Hydrian // New North: Weekly Meeting (new)',
    '{"Michael Jones","Taylor Doerbaum"}'::text[],
    2180,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87549285494?pwd=ibWG4xRLddaHqf8JzJ7T48gg886wbu.1',
    '{"id":"01KESXWXMZZDAX55BWVJNQFM01","title":"Hydrian // New North: Weekly Meeting (new)","summary":{"notes":"## **Survey Strategy and Engagement**\n\nThe team agreed to send a **custom reminder email** for the current SurveyMonkey survey on **Tuesday** to boost response rates without overwhelming recipients (05:15).  \n- **Taylor Doerbaum** proposed using SurveyMonkey’s native reminder feature to target unopened emails gently.  \n- **Michael Jones** suggested including initial response highlights in the reminder to encourage participation and show value.  \n- The reminder email’s wording will be drafted by Michael by **Friday morning** to ensure timely deployment.  \n- The approach aims to increase total responses beyond the current **4 within 24 hours**, improving data reliability for analysis and marketing use.  \n\nThe survey cadence will shift from monthly to **quarterly**, reflecting exhaustion of the initial question set and the need to integrate external data for richer insights (08:38).  \n- Michael explained that statistical questions require complex cross-industry data from **7 different companies**, complicating comparisons.  \n- Future surveys will slightly adjust questions but maintain core themes to build longitudinal benchmarking.  \n- Between survey cycles, the team will focus on producing marketing content from existing and newly gathered data.  \n\nTo increase survey accessibility, the team will add an **external survey link** in the upcoming newsletter, allowing recipients to click directly into the live survey (13:21).  \n- This external link feeds into the same SurveyMonkey database, ensuring data consolidation.  \n- Michael approved adding the link and emphasized the importance of monitoring subscriber engagement and response rates post-deployment.  \n\n## **Content and Newsletter Development**\n\nThe newsletter will launch **early next week**, featuring survey insights and a call to action linking to the current survey (15:13).  \n- Taylor will finalize the newsletter design incorporating Michael’s four posts and the external survey link.  \n- Michael prefers a **carousel-style post format** on LinkedIn for survey content, which increases engagement by breaking information into clickable slides (16:28).  \n- The carousel will cover individual survey questions like **growth and AI expectations**, highlighting key responses and trends per slide for easier consumption.  \n\nTaylor will create a **copy document and visual mockup** outlining slide headers and content flow, which Michael will review and refine to ensure clarity and impact (20:23).  \n- Michael aims to keep posts **non-salesy and insightful**, drawing from client work examples without revealing sensitive details.  \n- The strategy focuses on posting high-quality content **weekly** rather than daily, aiming to build sustained engagement and brand recall.  \n- Both agreed that shareable, forwardable content will help broaden the newsletter’s reach organically.  \n\n## **Booth Design and Marketing Collateral**\n\nMichael prefers **booth design option 4A** for its balanced branding and less aggressive tone compared to 4B (25:23).  \n- He highlighted the importance of placing the **Hydrion logo prominently at the top** for better brand recognition in busy environments.  \n- Michael requested resizing the **forklift icon** and aligning the “limited access” text on a single line for cleaner visuals (26:15).  \n- Taylor will adjust the icon size and layout and send an updated mockup for final approval.  \n\nRegarding the **one-pager brochure**, both agreed the current draft contains too much text and needs to be shortened into **three or four bullet points** for quick readability (29:05).  \n- The brochure should clearly explain the purpose of the QR codes and the free assessment while avoiding lengthy paragraphs.  \n- Michael emphasized the need for concise, actionable points that convey benefits like **improved fill rates** and **better profitability** at a glance.  \n- Taylor will coordinate with the design team to update the layout accordingly for use as a standalone handout.  \n\n## **Data and Analytics Preparation**\n\nMichael flagged potential gaps in the **most engaged firm spreadsheet**, noting the latest data appears to stop at **November** (32:15).  \n- Taylor will check with the developer to locate any updated traffic and engagement data, considering that exclusions may have moved some data to a new sheet (33:02).  \n- The team plans to pull detailed **web traffic insights**, including firm names and job titles, for the upcoming meeting on **February 28th** to inform marketing strategy.  \n- Michael stressed the importance of defining **clear success metrics and timelines** for campaign measurement during the February meeting (34:08).  \n\n## **Strategic Marketing Vision**\n\nMichael shared a developing marketing strategy focused on producing **thought leadership material** that provides clear, non-salesy insights to target audiences (10:57).  \n- He noted that inbound leads so far have mainly been **spam**, highlighting the need for valuable content to attract genuine interest.  \n- The strategy involves combining survey data with internal analytics to create **benchmark reports** and case studies that resonate with clients.  \n- Michael’s goal is to align expectations with realistic timelines and measurable outcomes, seeking input from Taylor and Josh to refine these plans (35:01).  \n\nTaylor and Michael agreed that defining **realistic goals and deadlines** is crucial for progress and accountability (35:14).  \n- The team will continue iterative content development and data analysis to support this vision.  \n- They plan ongoing collaboration on LinkedIn content and newsletter enhancements, with regular feedback loops to optimize engagement.","outline":null,"keywords":["SurveyMonkey","Newsletter","LinkedIn Carousel","Booth Design","Marketing Strategy","Web Traffic Data"],"overview":"- **Survey Strategy:** Reminder email for SurveyMonkey survey is set for Tuesday to boost response rates beyond current 4 returns.\n\n- **Quarterly Cadence:** Surveys shift to quarterly to integrate external data, maintaining core themes for longitudinal benchmarking.\n\n- **Newsletter Launch:** Newsletter launches next week with survey insights and a call to action linking to live survey.\n\n- **Booth Design:** Preferred booth design 4A emphasizes brand identity, with Hydrion logo prominently placed for recognition.\n\n- **One-Pager Revamp:** Brochure content must condense into 3-4 bullet points for quick readability; focus on benefits like improved fill rates.\n\n- **Data Gaps:** Potential data issues noted; request update on traffic and engagement data by February 28th for marketing strategy revisions.","action_items":"\n**Taylor Doerbaum**\nMonitor SurveyMonkey responses through Friday and prepare reminder email copy with initial survey insights for Michael to review by end of week (04:01)\nAdd external SurveyMonkey survey link to the closing section of upcoming Hydrian newsletter and finalize design for early next week distribution (13:21)\nCreate a LinkedIn carousel mockup using existing newsletter copy; prepare slide-by-slide copy outline and send it to Michael for review and additions (20:40)\nAdjust booth design per Michael’s feedback (reduce forklift icon size, reformat text to single line) and send updated mockup (24:55)\nCollaborate on revising one-pager brochure text to be more concise, bullet formatted, and explanatory of QR codes and assessments (28:55)\nCoordinate with developer to locate and retrieve the latest web traffic/exclusion data spreadsheet and share with Michael (31:20)\nShare final newsletter content draft and LinkedIn post ideas with Michael by Friday for feedback (35:32)\n\n**Michael Jones**\nReview survey data and provide initial impressions and wording guidance for reminder email by Friday (05:15)\nOffer feedback and finalize draft copy for LinkedIn carousel posts and newsletter content once Taylor sends mockups and drafts (20:40)\nDecide on booth design preference (favoring 4A) and provide icon size and layout feedback for the design team (24:55)\nAssess existing brochure versus one-pager designs to recommend text tightening and bullet list content (28:55)\nReview web traffic and engagement data once Taylor secures full dataset for preparation of March 28th meeting (31:20)\nPrepare strategic input and clarify realistic goals ahead of March 28th meeting (33:47)\n"},"duration":36.34000015258789,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Michael Jones"},{"id":1,"name":"Taylor Doerbaum"}],"sentences":[{"text":"There you go.","index":0,"end_time":4.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Hey, Michael.","index":1,"end_time":4.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":4.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Hello.","index":2,"end_time":5.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":5.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":3,"end_time":7.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":6.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"How are you?","index":4,"end_time":8.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I am dealing with some crazy allergies, so I don''t know, wondering what''s going on with my left eye.","index":5,"end_time":14.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":9.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, dear.","index":6,"end_time":15.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":14.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We.","index":7,"end_time":16.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":15.919,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We''ve had some crazy warm weather, which is normal to me in Texas, but everyone says it''s abnormally warm right now.","index":8,"end_time":23.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":16.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the cedar allergies are just horrible.","index":9,"end_time":26.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.44,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Today''s wind is like 40 mph wind.","index":10,"end_time":30.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":27.68,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So the pollen, every time I let my dog out, it''s just coming straight in the house.","index":11,"end_time":34.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So my left eye has been like super swollen all day.","index":12,"end_time":38.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":34.64,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, no.","index":13,"end_time":40.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, yes, I''ve been like dropping eye drops in there, but yes.","index":14,"end_time":45.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":40.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s been, it''s been crazy.","index":15,"end_time":47.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":45.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ve never had such insane allergies than, than down here because I grew up in New York where everything like dies off in the winter and you can kind of catch a break from that.","index":16,"end_time":56.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":47.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s true, actually.","index":17,"end_time":57.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":18,"end_time":57.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But not here.","index":19,"end_time":59.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":57.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"No.","index":20,"end_time":61.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, have you had.","index":21,"end_time":62.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"See, do you get allergies a lot then?","index":22,"end_time":64.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I never did, like growing up every now and then, but not nothing for like the past 10 years.","index":23,"end_time":70.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":65.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then since moving down here, I have had them pretty bad and it''s a bummer.","index":24,"end_time":75.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":70.38,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But this year''s definitely been the worst.","index":25,"end_time":76.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":75.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The past two weeks have been crazy.","index":26,"end_time":79.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":77.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But yeah, I went to go pick up eye drops and the pharmacist said that everybody around here is just suffering.","index":27,"end_time":86.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, there''s so much pollen.","index":28,"end_time":88.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":86.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t know how useful it is, but I will, I''ll share an ex.","index":29,"end_time":92.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''ll share my experience.","index":30,"end_time":93.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":92.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, I used to have terrible grass allergy.","index":31,"end_time":96.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, really, really bad.","index":32,"end_time":97.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":96.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, you know, you cut some grass somewhere and I''m tearing away and all the rest of it.","index":33,"end_time":101.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"My wife went ahead and got me into homeopathy and so I went to a homeopath and it was a very strange experience, but it solved the problem.","index":34,"end_time":115.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":102.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, actually it was two.","index":35,"end_time":116.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":115.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It was two things we.","index":36,"end_time":118.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":116.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I didn''t realize I had a milk allergy for years, but yeah, forever.","index":37,"end_time":123.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":118.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I had literally had it forever and I was always suffering and I never, never put the two and two together back in those days.","index":38,"end_time":128.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It wasn''t that well thought of or known.","index":39,"end_time":131.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And anyway, he, he went ahead and saw that one out, but the grass one was.","index":40,"end_time":137.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He put me on a course of homeopathic, literally over the counter homeopathic pills.","index":41,"end_time":143.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.95,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I haven''t had a problem since.","index":42,"end_time":146.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Do you know what they were?","index":43,"end_time":147.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":146.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is it like just natural, like supplements?","index":44,"end_time":150.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":147.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It was, I think it was euphrasia is what I took.","index":45,"end_time":154.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":150.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It depends.","index":46,"end_time":156.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":155.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s a very strange experience.","index":47,"end_time":157.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If you ever go to one.","index":48,"end_time":158.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":157.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s a very strange experience.","index":49,"end_time":159.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"They ask you some very odd questions.","index":50,"end_time":161.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":159.79,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Of course.","index":51,"end_time":162.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":52,"end_time":162.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''re taking a different route.","index":53,"end_time":164.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.84,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The whole point of homeopathy is to literally take.","index":54,"end_time":169.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Take the whole body backwards.","index":55,"end_time":171.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So it tries to work out what causes the allergy and it just takes the whole body backwards.","index":56,"end_time":176.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So it''s not, it''s not suppressant.","index":57,"end_time":179.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":176.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s basically trying to work out what it is and then literally reprogram the body to crazy be.","index":58,"end_time":186.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.08,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Be itself self sustained.","index":59,"end_time":188.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So you''re not relying on suppressing medication.","index":60,"end_time":191.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":188.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":61,"end_time":192.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":191.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s very good stuff.","index":62,"end_time":193.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Honestly, I have to say that''s one of the ones that I would go.","index":63,"end_time":196.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":193.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I''m pretty open to anything.","index":64,"end_time":198.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m not a real pull.","index":65,"end_time":200,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m not a real big pill taker.","index":66,"end_time":201.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":200,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":67,"end_time":202.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.12,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I''m.","index":68,"end_time":203.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We try to be as healthy as we can like most people.","index":69,"end_time":206.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, we try to sort of.","index":70,"end_time":208.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":206.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because we''re actually.","index":71,"end_time":209.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Because of milk.","index":72,"end_time":210,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":209.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"My wife is both milk and wheat.","index":73,"end_time":212.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So anything we look, anything we buy, we read ingredients.","index":74,"end_time":217.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then over the years we basically just ignore everything that we can''t pronounce and you know.","index":75,"end_time":222.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":76,"end_time":222.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I appreciate the recommendation.","index":77,"end_time":224.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":78,"end_time":224.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I feel like nowadays modern medicine is trying to kind of just suppress it.","index":79,"end_time":228.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":224.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like you said, it doesn''t fix.","index":80,"end_time":229.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":228.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It does.","index":81,"end_time":229.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":82,"end_time":229.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It just suppresses stuff and you know, it''s like I''m getting paid quite well by this pharmaceutical company.","index":83,"end_time":235.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":229.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Why don''t you try this drug?","index":84,"end_time":236.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":85,"end_time":238.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We all have to look into that.","index":86,"end_time":239.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":238.5,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we''ll see.","index":87,"end_time":241.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":239.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like I say, it''s.","index":88,"end_time":242.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":241.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s.","index":89,"end_time":242.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":242.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I. I''m sure everyone is different but if you ever go to a pharmacist or whatever like that, look at the homeopathic things because they do say what''s okay, useful for.","index":90,"end_time":253.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":242.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But like I say, I had to go to one because I didn''t have a clue.","index":91,"end_time":257.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":253.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And yeah, I''ll have to look into that.","index":92,"end_time":259.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":257.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s been so bad lately that I, I''m like walking into the pharmacist, like what do you have that will fix this?","index":93,"end_time":265.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''ll see.","index":94,"end_time":268.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":266.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But anyway, I do appreciate it.","index":95,"end_time":270.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":268.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So with this survey monkey that we had sent out yesterday morning, I just checked a little bit earlier.","index":96,"end_time":280.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":273.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we''re up to 4 responses now within 24 hours.","index":97,"end_time":283.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I have some stats that SurveyMonkey has given me so far with who''s opened.","index":98,"end_time":288.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":283.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We have a lot that remain unopened.","index":99,"end_time":290.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":288.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think that what would be best is I''ve been Doing some research to see how to kind of work with SurveyMonkey directly to set like a reminder.","index":100,"end_time":298.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":291.41,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I think it would just be beneficial.","index":101,"end_time":300.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"There''s a way you can just do a custom reminder that I can send out Tuesday that just resends the survey to kind of maybe reach the people that haven''t opened it.","index":102,"end_time":309.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":300.2,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it''s not a whole nother long email that, you know, poking at them.","index":103,"end_time":313,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.28,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But wanted to get your input on that before I went ahead.","index":104,"end_time":315.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":313,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Absolutely, totally.","index":105,"end_time":316.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I do wonder if it''s something that we might want to look at.","index":106,"end_time":321.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":316.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Imagine before you send it.","index":107,"end_time":324.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":321.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And you don''t need that much time to sort of get the text together.","index":108,"end_time":327.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":324.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If we look, imagine we got five or six responses and we were able to sort of put some sort of initial anecdotal thoughts together on the responses.","index":109,"end_time":336.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":327.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, we could write something along the lines as a reminder, you know, you did receive a survey, we really appreciate it, blah, blah, blah.","index":110,"end_time":344.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":337.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Initial findings are this, you know.","index":111,"end_time":347.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.28,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":112,"end_time":348.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":347.92,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And that''s really encouraging.","index":113,"end_time":349.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":348.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, you know, the more you can contribute, the more of a statistical thing we can get.","index":114,"end_time":354.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":349.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And obviously we will then share the results back with you.","index":115,"end_time":357.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":116,"end_time":358.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":357.47,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because I think Josh and myself were talking about this quite a lot recently and a lot of what we''re trying to think about is trying to give really interesting insights as a way of saying thanks very much for doing something for us, but results.","index":117,"end_time":372.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":358.43,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And we haven''t been very good at doing that.","index":118,"end_time":374.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":372.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I know we''ve been.","index":119,"end_time":374.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":374.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve been promising the world, but we haven''t been able to do a thing.","index":120,"end_time":378.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":375.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I''m really trying to do more of that.","index":121,"end_time":381.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":378.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So that would be my only caveat is.","index":122,"end_time":384.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.23,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, when you say, right, I need some words, Michael.","index":123,"end_time":387.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":384.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Tomorrow, you know, latest, we''ll have a look at the survey, we''ll put some thoughts together and then we''ll get that back to you.","index":124,"end_time":395.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":388.51,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, let me.","index":125,"end_time":396.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Let''s give it a little bit longer to see how many come in so we can pull that data.","index":126,"end_time":399.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":396.39,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s super easy to set up in SurveyMonkey.","index":127,"end_time":402.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s been very easy to use.","index":128,"end_time":403.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":402.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if we just want to see, I can come up with like a.","index":129,"end_time":406.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":403.79,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Just a quick outline of what that could look like.","index":130,"end_time":408.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then Friday, if we just want to take a look in the morning at what we''ve gotten in, and if we don''t even.","index":131,"end_time":413.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":408.71,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Honestly, if you wanted to give it over the weekend till Monday, it''s very easy to just plug it into the SurveyMonkey platform.","index":132,"end_time":419.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":413.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can schedule that Monday for Tuesday.","index":133,"end_time":421.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we can give it more time to kind of get some more results in.","index":134,"end_time":426.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I don''t really know how this typically works.","index":135,"end_time":428.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":426.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, I suppose if you get an email, you open it there and then, or you might open it the next day, but then you probably won''t open it.","index":136,"end_time":435.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":428.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, Friday makes sense to me.","index":137,"end_time":438.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So we can wait until Friday.","index":138,"end_time":440.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":139,"end_time":440.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":440.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Check it out and then I can give you some words if you just want to give me some guidance on of course, how you want the email to look and I can fill in the gaps.","index":140,"end_time":449.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":440.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We can do that.","index":141,"end_time":450.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":449.49,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes, that sounds great.","index":142,"end_time":451.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":450.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Good.","index":143,"end_time":452.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":451.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":144,"end_time":452.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":452.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Like this.","index":145,"end_time":453.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":452.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yes.","index":146,"end_time":454.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so then the other thing, I know I mentioned this last week, but we''re going to warm up some new domains.","index":147,"end_time":458.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Something that I did notice.","index":148,"end_time":459.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I tested this Survey monkey like three times before we launched this because it was a new platform and we just wanted to check it out a couple of times with a URL attached to like via Survey Monkey.","index":149,"end_time":470.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":459.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It will immediately go to spam and so we''re trying to prevent that from happening.","index":150,"end_time":474.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":470.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I went ahead and marked it as not spam as many places as I could and it did deliver to obviously a bunch of inboxes where people did open it because I don''t think people are necessarily checking their spam every day.","index":151,"end_time":486.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":475.95,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s good to see that it''s not all ending up that way.","index":152,"end_time":490.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":486.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But with these new domains we''re hoping to replace it in that way to kind of give it like a fresh URL.","index":153,"end_time":498.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":490.67,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And that''s supposed to help, especially using the smartly domains that we''re warming up because the mailforge one previously had a couple of errors.","index":154,"end_time":505.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.32,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we will swap those out for the next one.","index":155,"end_time":507.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":505.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I did want to ask, I know originally when we talked about this it was going to be a month to month survey.","index":156,"end_time":512.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":507.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is that still.","index":157,"end_time":513.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":512.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The idea is that there''ll be a February one.","index":158,"end_time":515.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":513.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Are you thinking every other month?","index":159,"end_time":517.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":515.4,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":160,"end_time":518.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.6,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The thing is, I think it would have turned out like that, but it will actually become quarterly in the end.","index":161,"end_time":524.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":518.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Here''s where we are.","index":162,"end_time":527.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So from that large spreadsheet that we originally pulled from, I think we''ve exhausted the questionnaires.","index":163,"end_time":537.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":528.02,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ve got what, 10 questions.","index":164,"end_time":539.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":537.54,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I think we''ve exhausted that one to date, but we should be looking at this more.","index":165,"end_time":544.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":539.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But the other bit that we have is a whole bunch of statistical questions which we aren''t putting out.","index":166,"end_time":551.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":546.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We try and fudge those with existing data that we have from our clients.","index":167,"end_time":556.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That''s proving slightly more difficult to pull together because not every single company we work with every single company in the same sort of way.","index":168,"end_time":570.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":558.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Not everyone has a standard set of reporting a standard set of way we utilize data, it''s hard to do a comparison.","index":169,"end_time":578.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":570.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So we''ve pulled from seven different companies, but they''re all different industries.","index":170,"end_time":583.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":578.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So that''s making it slightly difficult for us to then look at the numbers and try and make something up.","index":171,"end_time":588.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We probably think based upon what we''re seeing, we think we can make a fairly good guess of what''s actually happening within the markets in terms of different ways they see things.","index":172,"end_time":604.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":589.37,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I think we should be okay.","index":173,"end_time":606.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So my premise, or our thoughts was to have the questions going to the survey and then the data, and then build the two together and actually produce a report again, that''s taken far too long.","index":174,"end_time":622.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":606.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So answer your question.","index":175,"end_time":624.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":623.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I would say as soon as this one''s done, we either think of more questions and then we send it out again, or we utilize the time to then produce material for supporting marketing.","index":176,"end_time":641.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then the quarter comes around and we''ll do the whole thing again.","index":177,"end_time":645.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":642.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So maybe in March we would send the whole lot.","index":178,"end_time":649.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We''ll slightly tweak the questions, but they''re very much asking a similar sort of thing.","index":179,"end_time":654.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then we get some more material back, right?","index":180,"end_time":657.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":655.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":181,"end_time":657.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think it''s like this one''s done and then we''ve got a bit of a gap.","index":182,"end_time":661.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":657.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But we do want to go ahead and start producing more material that can go into the marketing activities that we do.","index":183,"end_time":669.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":661.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So this is actually a very, very quick segue because I only sent it to you five minutes ago, but I developed a thought process around marketing strategy for us, and I went ahead and thought, well, I''ll share this with you, I think.","index":184,"end_time":685.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":669.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":185,"end_time":687.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":686.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think it''s a good one.","index":186,"end_time":688.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":687.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s very.","index":187,"end_time":689.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":688.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s everything that we''ve spoken about already.","index":188,"end_time":691.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":689.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"There''s nothing here that''s new, but it''s a different way.","index":189,"end_time":695.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":691.36,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we should be looking at how to grow Hydrion in a different way.","index":190,"end_time":702.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So we talked about leads and all the rest of it, just not happening.","index":191,"end_time":706.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.24,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But funny enough, I know I keep on jumping around.","index":192,"end_time":709.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":707.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know if you''ve noticed, but all these.","index":193,"end_time":712.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":710.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"These times when we''ve actually had people come to us, filled out forms have all been spam.","index":194,"end_time":718.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":712.89,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":195,"end_time":719.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":718.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Every single time the woman I spoke to from that indoor firm, she goes, yes, look.","index":196,"end_time":725.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":719.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"She said it wasn''t me.","index":197,"end_time":726.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":725.41,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I have not filled this in.","index":198,"end_time":727.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":726.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"She said, I''m getting calls from everyone in the moment.","index":199,"end_time":729.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And she was from like csr, which is what the corporate responsibility Department.","index":200,"end_time":736.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":730.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So it has nothing to do with that, us at all.","index":201,"end_time":738.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I can''t even engage a conversation with her about, well, what''s going on with your firm because she just didn''t want to talk to me.","index":202,"end_time":744.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":738.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":203,"end_time":744.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":744.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, you know, that''s, that''s interesting in itself.","index":204,"end_time":749.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So the reason I''m bringing this up is that a lot of what we need to do is we need to produce some very, very clever thought leadership type material that will support all the different avenues that we want to go down.","index":205,"end_time":763.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":749.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And survey is an important part of that.","index":206,"end_time":766.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":763.65,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":207,"end_time":767.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":767.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Okay.","index":208,"end_time":768.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":768.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But it''s going to take us a while to get to a good place where we can hopefully get some good feedback, you know, use more data that we have internally to do some more analysis and support the work and then start to go ahead and start to build out some benchmarks, give you more and more material that you can utilize, repurpose across the different groups that we work.","index":209,"end_time":793.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":768.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, we can still do more on the survey, but it might take us a little bit more to develop.","index":210,"end_time":800.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":793.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":211,"end_time":801.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":801.06,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Understandably.","index":212,"end_time":802.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":801.54,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, yeah, sounds good.","index":213,"end_time":804.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":802.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Great.","index":214,"end_time":808.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As far as the newsletter, I got that link from you.","index":215,"end_time":811.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":809.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I thought it was really great that you had like the insight into each of the questions that you had added here.","index":216,"end_time":818.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":811.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''ll be really good.","index":217,"end_time":819.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":818.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"The only thing I would say we should add is with the survey monkey that I created, they do give me an option to use an external link.","index":218,"end_time":827.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so I have this external link that will feed into the same database with the responses.","index":219,"end_time":831.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":827.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So I was thinking that maybe we could just add it in to the closing of this newsletter so that people who get this newsletter can click that link and take the current survey that we have running and get some additional.","index":220,"end_time":845.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":832.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, Things into there so we can wordsmith that into there.","index":221,"end_time":849.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":845.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But we do have a, a link that will direct directly to the same database.","index":222,"end_time":853.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":849.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Actually, this is like the fourth or fifth iteration where it was Josh going, saying, I''ll put the questions in.","index":223,"end_time":860.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I said, I don''t want to do that.","index":224,"end_time":861.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.31,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s going to turn into a very long thing.","index":225,"end_time":863.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":861.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"He goes, oh, no, people are going to be very interested in that.","index":226,"end_time":864.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":863.15,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I go, okay.","index":227,"end_time":865.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":864.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Oh my God.","index":228,"end_time":868.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.39,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, so before I had one which was, you know, very much sort of narrative based, and it sort of took in, it had certain percentages than another one which had more percentages and something else and something else.","index":229,"end_time":879.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":868.11,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then finally, because again, I''ve got to get his sign off because again, it''s important that we do.","index":230,"end_time":885.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":879.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I can''t just do everything without him, you know, having the input.","index":231,"end_time":888.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":885.2,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So, yes.","index":232,"end_time":889.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":888.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"You know, I mean, if.","index":233,"end_time":890.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":889.56,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If this is.","index":234,"end_time":891.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":890.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If this is a format that works, then what.","index":235,"end_time":893.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":891.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Whatever.","index":236,"end_time":894.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":893.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, it''d be interesting to sort of see the feedback that we get from this.","index":237,"end_time":898.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":894.52,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, people have opened it.","index":238,"end_time":900.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":898.04,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If we get new subscribers to it, whatever it may be.","index":239,"end_time":903.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":900.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":240,"end_time":904.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":903.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If we do, then great, it worked.","index":241,"end_time":905.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I''m happy as hell.","index":242,"end_time":907.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":905.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":243,"end_time":907.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":907.45,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"All for it.","index":244,"end_time":908.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":907.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Add that link.","index":245,"end_time":909.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":908.69,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":246,"end_time":910.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then.","index":247,"end_time":911.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":910.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Do you have a particular timeline of when you would like this to go out?","index":248,"end_time":917.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":913.53,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Is there a specific time or just any time?","index":249,"end_time":918.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":917.17,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"As soon as we can get it in the design and maybe early next week?","index":250,"end_time":921.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":918.81,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I think so.","index":251,"end_time":922.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":921.85,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":252,"end_time":923.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":922.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t think any.","index":253,"end_time":924.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":923.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t think anyone has it in their calendar that the Hydra newsletter is going to drop in their inbox for the first time.","index":254,"end_time":928.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":924.05,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"They''re waiting patiently.","index":255,"end_time":929.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":928.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Ringing me up, going, what else?","index":256,"end_time":932.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":931.82,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Newsletter.","index":257,"end_time":933.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"That would be great.","index":258,"end_time":936.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":935.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, that sounds good.","index":259,"end_time":938.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":260,"end_time":939.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":938.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We will input that into the design and add that little blurb at the end with the link and then the content, which was great too, to get from me, those four posts.","index":261,"end_time":948.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Did you want to create just individual us to create just individual images that we normally do, or were you wanting to maybe make it kind of a carousel thing?","index":262,"end_time":955.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":948.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I know I sent that.","index":263,"end_time":956.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":955.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I didn''t quite understand that.","index":264,"end_time":958.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":956.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":265,"end_time":958.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":958.46,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I am glad you brought that up.","index":266,"end_time":961.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":959.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, I did see the examples and I thought, okay, I love the examples.","index":267,"end_time":965.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":961.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I just couldn''t quite get my head around does it every time we put a post up, it''s just a different image or so.","index":268,"end_time":972.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":965.01,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It''s just like a. I think I have it in my email.","index":269,"end_time":976.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They grab the actual LinkedIn link.","index":270,"end_time":978.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":976.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It would just be one post.","index":271,"end_time":981.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":979.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I mean, we can make it into a series if you wanted it to.","index":272,"end_time":983.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":981.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"To go that way.","index":273,"end_time":984.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":983.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But it would be me.","index":274,"end_time":987.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.93,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I say, I just need to understand how it worked.","index":275,"end_time":989.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.07,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I couldn''t.","index":276,"end_time":990.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":989.91,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I saw the images and I just could not get my head around it at all.","index":277,"end_time":993.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":990.47,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So if we took one of like these posts that you had created, where we''re talking about just something, some kind of copy, we would just put it in like a normal post and then the way it''s uploaded in is tiny, like a PDF, but basically people just click through.","index":278,"end_time":1011.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":994.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s essentially we''re attaching five images that work together.","index":279,"end_time":1014.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1011.35,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So, like, it''ll say step one here, step two, step three.","index":280,"end_time":1018.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But in this case it could.","index":281,"end_time":1020.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1019.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"This is just an idea, but if you did like Q1, Q2, Q3, what we noticed in the industry, it would just be like a slide of that and so you could just put like a blur above.","index":282,"end_time":1030.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like in Q1 we noticed this about inventory.","index":283,"end_time":1034.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.51,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"In Q2 we noticed this.","index":284,"end_time":1035.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1034.03,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or yeah, just things like that.","index":285,"end_time":1038.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1035.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it''s just a way for people to interact with your post.","index":286,"end_time":1042.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1038.99,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They''re clicking through it.","index":287,"end_time":1043.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1042.58,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So instead of putting it all into just a piece of copy that people have to read through, it kind of tends to increase engagement because it''s more of a visual, engaging thing to look through.","index":288,"end_time":1053.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1044.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Obviously this one is for a accounting company, but we could create it so it resembles kind of how our newsletter images look.","index":289,"end_time":1063.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1054.18,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And it''s just a short blurb for each screen that you click through.","index":290,"end_time":1067.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It has like a, you know, glide to the next thing.","index":291,"end_time":1070.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1067.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"They look different for each industry that I work with, obviously, because everyone''s doing something different.","index":292,"end_time":1076.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1071.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s just an interactive way to put out content that''s not just, you know, a bunch of words on a screen.","index":293,"end_time":1084.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1077.02,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It just tends to try and visualize this.","index":294,"end_time":1087.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1084.379,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If we took the first post, which was about growth, I think it was, you''d still have that, but then would you have the.","index":295,"end_time":1095.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1087.34,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The four or the three be this case would be three other slides.","index":296,"end_time":1101.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1095.58,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Would they all talk about AI and this and that and the other.","index":297,"end_time":1106.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1102.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"They would talk about the next set of posts.","index":298,"end_time":1109.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1106.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Or it can be.","index":299,"end_time":1111.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1109.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"However, if these go together, I didn''t have a chance to read through these yet.","index":300,"end_time":1114.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1111.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"If they all go together, then it could be one carousel.","index":301,"end_time":1118.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But if, like, AI Expectations versus reality is a topic that you feel like you could speak to, where each of these slides just talks about AI versus reality, then we would just make one post on that topic instead of like you''re saying, tying all of these in as one.","index":302,"end_time":1133.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1118.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It doesn''t have to be that way.","index":303,"end_time":1135.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1133.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We could just pick one topic to do.","index":304,"end_time":1136.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1135.01,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"What about if we went ahead and took growth?","index":305,"end_time":1139.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1137.33,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"What we could do is that we could maybe utilize some of the answers.","index":306,"end_time":1145.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1140.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So in other words, so growth is like the first question, it''s question one, and then you''ve got four.","index":307,"end_time":1154.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1147.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think we had like six different responses or six different answers.","index":308,"end_time":1158.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1154.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":309,"end_time":1159.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1158.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":310,"end_time":1160.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1159.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Things.","index":311,"end_time":1160.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1160.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We could do that, but we could utilize maybe that.","index":312,"end_time":1165.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The text I put in the newsletter.","index":313,"end_time":1167.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1165.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If there''s not enough material, we could add more material to it.","index":314,"end_time":1170.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1167.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":315,"end_time":1171.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1171.3,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Would that make more sense?","index":316,"end_time":1173.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1172.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then the next one about AI would be exactly the same.","index":317,"end_time":1175.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1173.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So AI and then, you know, we are six questions.","index":318,"end_time":1179.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1175.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We asked these people, and then these are the six questions.","index":319,"end_time":1181.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1179.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then this was really important.","index":320,"end_time":1183.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1181.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Then this was really important.","index":321,"end_time":1184.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1183.67,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"This was less important.","index":322,"end_time":1185.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1184.75,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Then you''d have, you know, real insightful, sort of Things we could certainly do.","index":323,"end_time":1190.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1185.59,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We could do that.","index":324,"end_time":1190.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1190.19,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, that''s a good way to do it because then people again, like the idea is to increase the engagement.","index":325,"end_time":1197.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1190.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if you''re saying like on the intro image here you would explain what it is and like it could say like swipe to see what people cared less about or what people care more about.","index":326,"end_time":1207.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1197.11,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It''s like, okay, I''m like interested in what that part would be.","index":327,"end_time":1209.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1207.07,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So it kind of keeps them going through.","index":328,"end_time":1211.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1209.27,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But I can create like a, we''ll create like a mockup of it.","index":329,"end_time":1214.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Since you already did the work of the copy.","index":330,"end_time":1216.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1214.55,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It would just be us throwing together some images.","index":331,"end_time":1219.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1216.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So we also need some words as well, don''t we?","index":332,"end_time":1222.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1219.35,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":333,"end_time":1223.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So yeah, but I can just pull from what you have in here and then I''ll go through the newsletter, I''ll send you a copy example, I''ll like, you know, write out how it would be designed and I''ll send that over to you to add anything additional that I left out.","index":334,"end_time":1237.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1223.23,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Love that.","index":335,"end_time":1238.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1237.77,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think that''s a great idea.","index":336,"end_time":1239.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1238.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":337,"end_time":1240.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1239.77,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Again, you know, I refer back to that document.","index":338,"end_time":1242.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So I spent, I would say the last couple of weeks learning.","index":339,"end_time":1247.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1242.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I''m just trying to learn as much as I possibly can.","index":340,"end_time":1252.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1249.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I''m thinking, oh, this is really interesting.","index":341,"end_time":1254.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1252.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And one of the things that I was sort of trying to work out was best practices within like small medium sized consulting firms.","index":342,"end_time":1261.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1254.29,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And one of the things, it''s pretty much what you guys have been saying for some time, which is about, you know, the insights but you know, it''s trying to give them non salesy stuff that''s really insightful, that makes them remember.","index":343,"end_time":1276.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1262.3,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think we need to do more of that sort of.","index":344,"end_time":1280.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1277.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":345,"end_time":1280.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1280.22,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Front of mind, not.","index":346,"end_time":1282.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1280.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then one of the other things is maybe sort of like we don''t have to post every single day even if we posted once and once a week.","index":347,"end_time":1289.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.62,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"But it''s going to be something that they go, oh, that''s really interesting.","index":348,"end_time":1293.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1290.05,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, and it gets posted because it gets, don''t forget it''s still getting posted three times because it gets posted to all of ours and then away we go.","index":349,"end_time":1302.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1293.21,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So it''s not just LinkedIn page, but it''s to Josh and to Drew and to myself and, And I do think that that''s good that we can, we, you know, the more material we could do because I think we''ve been struggling quite a lot with material.","index":350,"end_time":1317.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1302.57,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it''s almost.","index":351,"end_time":1319.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1318.22,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Sometimes it was just too anecdotal because one of the things I''m going to try and do more of is.","index":352,"end_time":1324.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Is try to give you more what we are doing with a client right now without giving state secrets away, you know, and then we can say, right, can we build this case study or can we.","index":353,"end_time":1335.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Rather than worrying about building something that takes forever.","index":354,"end_time":1338.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1335.99,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If I said, okay, look, the flavor of the month at the moment appears to be blank.","index":355,"end_time":1344.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1339.27,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, let''s do something with that, you know, and so we, we, we start to do those sorts of things, you know.","index":356,"end_time":1351.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.55,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":357,"end_time":1352.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1351.989,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I always like to put myself like in the audience''s shoes, like what would be compelling to me.","index":358,"end_time":1356.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1352.31,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And so anytime I''m on LinkedIn, because we do LinkedIn posts for a lot of our clients, like if I''m just catching up on my timeline in feed, I try to like, think about as I''m going through, like, what''s standing out to me.","index":359,"end_time":1366.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1356.87,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And these types of posts are way more.","index":360,"end_time":1369.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1366.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''m way more prone to stop and look through these than I am when it''s just like a giant blurb of text because I might not have as much time or it might not like stand out to me, but if I see something that I can indirectly click through and it applies to, you know, what work I''m in or it''s just interesting, like, especially with survey results, it''s interesting to hear what other people are thinking or saying or like how their business is going.","index":361,"end_time":1391.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1369.59,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because I find myself sometimes on LinkedIn looking at posts about industries that I have nothing to do with, but it''s just interesting.","index":362,"end_time":1396.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1391.7,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And then if you know somebody who knows somebody, they might end up sending it.","index":363,"end_time":1400.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.74,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And, and it kind of just works that way so well.","index":364,"end_time":1403.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1400.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":365,"end_time":1404.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1403.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Which, which does lead to some of the things I was reading about is, is getting people to forward things.","index":366,"end_time":1409.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1404.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, this is interesting.","index":367,"end_time":1410.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.38,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think they might find this useful to read, you know, that sort of stuff.","index":368,"end_time":1415.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1411.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I think we need to get more of those sorts of.","index":369,"end_time":1418.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1415.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Of.","index":370,"end_time":1419.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1419.14,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yes.","index":371,"end_time":1419.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1419.34,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Pieces of work is a momentum, you know.","index":372,"end_time":1422.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1420.26,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":373,"end_time":1423.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1422.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I just sort of looking at this one here, and you got 58 responses and it''s an accounting firm, you know, and you think, hang on, there''s millions of accounting firms a lot, everywhere.","index":374,"end_time":1433.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1424.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Right.","index":375,"end_time":1434.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1434.42,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Why is this suddenly making such a difference?","index":376,"end_time":1437.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1434.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, unless it''s 58 people that work with the firm, which is slightly different, but if it isn''t, that''s even better.","index":377,"end_time":1443.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1437.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"You know, this had really good traction.","index":378,"end_time":1445.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1443.46,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"66 total.","index":379,"end_time":1446.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1445.78,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":380,"end_time":1449.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1446.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So just kind of changing up the content is a good thing to do.","index":381,"end_time":1454.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1449.98,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":382,"end_time":1455.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1454.7,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Done the same thing for so long, it could get Fatigued.","index":383,"end_time":1457.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1455.26,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So that''s how I was thinking is maybe we could just work a carousel in and.","index":384,"end_time":1461.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1457.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And see how that performs.","index":385,"end_time":1462.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1461.1,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I love it.","index":386,"end_time":1463.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1462.94,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So if you want to.","index":387,"end_time":1465.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1463.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If you want to make the main body text shorter, by all means do so.","index":388,"end_time":1470.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1465.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"If you want to take what we do and just say, right, I''m only going to use the first whatever sentence because it''s compelling and it''s like, in your face.","index":389,"end_time":1478.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1470.18,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then the rest we could put in the carousel.","index":390,"end_time":1481.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1478.93,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Let me know.","index":391,"end_time":1481.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1481.13,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Just.","index":392,"end_time":1481.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1481.53,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Just whatever you think makes sense.","index":393,"end_time":1483.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1481.73,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":394,"end_time":1483.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1483.57,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I''ll put it out into a copy doc to show you.","index":395,"end_time":1485.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1483.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Like, which up, slide 1, slide 2, slide 3.","index":396,"end_time":1488.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1485.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"And I''ll build it out that way and then let, like, header copy and we''ll go from there.","index":397,"end_time":1492.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1488.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":398,"end_time":1493.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.17,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Love it.","index":399,"end_time":1494.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.81,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Great.","index":400,"end_time":1495.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.25,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''s exciting.","index":401,"end_time":1496.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.73,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"That''ll be fun.","index":402,"end_time":1497.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1496.45,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Great.","index":403,"end_time":1499.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1499.33,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So then, I know you wanted some time to look over these, so I just put it in case you had any questions.","index":404,"end_time":1503.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1499.69,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But if you don''t have anything yet, we can.","index":405,"end_time":1505.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1503.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Or the booth design.","index":406,"end_time":1506.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1505.66,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I did drop this because I got Josh is similar to me A and B.","index":407,"end_time":1511.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1506.78,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay, so can we just have a look at that one quickly?","index":408,"end_time":1515.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1511.9,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I did drop it up to everybody else just to give some thoughts, but I think everyone''s so busy today, I don''t think they get it.","index":409,"end_time":1521.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1515.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Do you want to get this thing knocked on the head?","index":410,"end_time":1523.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1521.5,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So this is 4A.","index":411,"end_time":1525.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1523.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Oh, 4A.","index":412,"end_time":1527.926,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1526.86,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"4A.","index":413,"end_time":1528.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1528.074,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":414,"end_time":1529.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1528.74,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"4A and B.","index":415,"end_time":1529.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1529.06,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So what''s B look like?","index":416,"end_time":1532.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1531.32,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I can''t remember what B looks like.4B.","index":417,"end_time":1534.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1532.72,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"So it just removes.","index":418,"end_time":1536.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1535.48,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m gonna disagree with Josh.","index":419,"end_time":1539.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1536.68,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think 4A is better.","index":420,"end_time":1542.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1539.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Okay.","index":421,"end_time":1543.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1543.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"I think that''s too much.","index":422,"end_time":1544.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1543.64,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"In your face.","index":423,"end_time":1545,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1544.4,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Kill.","index":424,"end_time":1545.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1545.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Eliminate.","index":425,"end_time":1547.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1546.76,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, a little bit like.","index":426,"end_time":1549.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1547.88,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"All right, calm down.","index":427,"end_time":1553.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.96,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I like this one as well, a little bit better because you have the logo here, too, for logo recognition.","index":428,"end_time":1558.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1553.72,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Because right now, like, the way this is set up is everything is below.","index":429,"end_time":1562.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1558.6,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So if somebody''s walking by and your booth, like, your stand is right here, they might not see the hydrant.","index":430,"end_time":1569.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1562.91,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"But at least with this one, you have the logo up here for that brand recognition aspect.","index":431,"end_time":1574.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1569.19,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So on this one here, the only thing I would suggest is if we could make the.","index":432,"end_time":1579.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1575.789,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I emailed this to you, so apologies for repeating myself.","index":433,"end_time":1582.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1579.63,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"The forklift icon, can you make it smaller?","index":434,"end_time":1586.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1582.83,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And so a limited access is on the same line.","index":435,"end_time":1590.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1586.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Is that visually better than the way it is right now?","index":436,"end_time":1594.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1591.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":437,"end_time":1595.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1594.48,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I see what you''re saying.","index":438,"end_time":1596.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1595.08,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"So make this one sentence across.","index":439,"end_time":1597.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1596.04,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Make it one sentence.","index":440,"end_time":1598.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1597.8,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":441,"end_time":1599.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1598.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And then make this slightly smaller because, yeah, we can mess with that icon''s okay.","index":442,"end_time":1603.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1599.16,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I can''t think of a different icon, to be honest.","index":443,"end_time":1607.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1604.84,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, we can move it down, I think, and just.","index":444,"end_time":1611.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1609.16,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can''t make it slightly smaller.","index":445,"end_time":1613.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1611.88,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":446,"end_time":1615.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can mess with it because I.","index":447,"end_time":1617.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1615.21,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Think we made it smaller and because there we go.","index":448,"end_time":1620.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1617.09,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":449,"end_time":1620.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.49,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I mean, I have no idea how design things work, but.","index":450,"end_time":1623.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1620.97,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Do you?","index":451,"end_time":1625.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1624.37,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah, we can definitely change that.","index":452,"end_time":1627.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1625.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"We can make it smaller and move that over that way.","index":453,"end_time":1631.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1627.97,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"It is the same as this one where we have the one line period.","index":454,"end_time":1635.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1631.89,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"One line period.","index":455,"end_time":1636.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1635.61,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":456,"end_time":1637.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1637.25,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I think that would make more sense.","index":457,"end_time":1638.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1637.61,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I like that.","index":458,"end_time":1640.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1639.98,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"I don''t like B.","index":459,"end_time":1642.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1641.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"And I''m going to argue with Josh.","index":460,"end_time":1644.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1642.42,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"We shouldn''t have B, because I think B is too.","index":461,"end_time":1646.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1644.14,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"It looks to me it''s destructive.","index":462,"end_time":1648.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1647.1,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s aggressive.","index":463,"end_time":1650.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1648.86,"speaker_name":"Michael Jones"},{"text":"Yeah, it is aggressive.","index":464,"end_time":1652.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1650.9,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"With this here.","index":465,"end_time":1655.139,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1653.82,"speaker_name":"Taylor Doerbaum"},{"text":"Do you love this here?","index":466,"end_time":1656.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.139,"spea